## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-117">ABA 路由號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-117">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-118">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-118">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-119">九位數，可能是格式已格式化或未格式化的圖樣</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-119">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-120">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-120">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-121">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-121">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-122">以 0、1、2、3、6、7 或 8 開頭的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-122">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-123">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-123">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-124">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-124">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-125">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-126">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-126">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-127">未格式化：以 0、1、2、3、6、7 或 8 為開頭的九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-127">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-128">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-128">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-129">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-129">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-130">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-130">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-131">如果接近 300 個字元時，有一個策略會中信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-131">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-132">函數函數Func_aba_routing找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-132">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-133">系統找到Keyword_ABA_Routing關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-133">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-134">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-134">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-135">函數函數Func_aba_routing找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-135">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-149">路由號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-149">routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-150">路由傳輸號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-150">routing transit number</span></span>

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-153">阿根廷國家/ (身分識別) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-153">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-154">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-154">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-155">包含或不含句號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-155">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-156">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-156">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-157">八位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-157">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-158">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-158">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-159">選擇性期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-159">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-160">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-160">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-161">選擇性期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-161">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-162">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-162">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-163">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-164">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-164">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-165">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-166">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-166">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-167">正則運算式會Regex_argentina_national_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-167">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-168">系統找到Keyword_argentina_national_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-168">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-180">澳大利亞銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-180">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-181">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-181">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-182">包含或不含銀行州分行號碼的六到十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-182">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-183">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-183">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-184">帳號是 6 到 10 位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-184">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-185">澳洲銀行州分行號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-185">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-186">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-186">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-187">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-187">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-188">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-188">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-189">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-189">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-190">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-190">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-191">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-191">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-192">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-192">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-193">正則運算式會Regex_australia_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-194">系統找到Keyword_australia_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-195">正則運算式會Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-196">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-196">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-197">正則運算式會Regex_australia_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-198">系統找到Keyword_australia_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-198">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-204">usa account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-204">usa account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-205">擁有者位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-205">holder address</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-206">銀行位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-206">bank address</span></span>

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-214">澳大利亞商務號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-214">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-215">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-215">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-216">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-216">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-217">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-217">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-218">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-218">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-219">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-219">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-220">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-220">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-221">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-222">11 位數與選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-222">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-223">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-223">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-224">11 位數與選擇性分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-224">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-225">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-225">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-226">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-227">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-227">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-228">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-228">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-229">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-229">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-230">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-230">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-231">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-231">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-232">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-232">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-233">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-233">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-234">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-234">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-235">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-235">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-236">函數Func_australian_business_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-236">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-237">系統找到Keywords_australian_business_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-237">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-238">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-238">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-239">函數Func_australian_business_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-239">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-company-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-249">澳大利亞公司編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-249">Australia company number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-250">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-250">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-251">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-251">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-252">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-252">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-253">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-253">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-254">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-254">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-255">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-255">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-256">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-256">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-257">包含分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-257">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-258">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-258">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-259">包含分隔符號的九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-259">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-260">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-260">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-261">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-261">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-262">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-262">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-263">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-263">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-264">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-264">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-265">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-265">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-266">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-266">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-267">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-267">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-268">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-268">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-269">函數函數Func_Australian_Company_Number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-269">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-270">系統找到Keyword_Australian_Company_Number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-270">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-271">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-271">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-272">函數函數Func_Australian_Company_Number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-272">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-273">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-273">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-274">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-274">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-275">可以</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-275">acn</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-276">澳大利亞公司否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-276">australia company no</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-282">澳大利亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-282">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-283">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-283">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-284">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-284">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-285">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-285">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-286">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-286">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-287">兩位數或兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-287">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-288">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-288">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-289">五位數或五位數的字母 (大小寫不區分) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-289">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-290">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-290">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-291">選擇一到兩個不區分大小寫 (字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-291">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-292">四到九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-292">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-293">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-293">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-294">九位數或九位數的字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-294">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-295">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-296">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-296">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-297">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-298">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-298">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-299">正則運算式會Regex_australia_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-299">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-300">系統找到Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-300">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-301">找不到來自Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-301">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-401">澳大利亞醫療帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-401">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-402">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-403">10-11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-403">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-404">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-405">10-11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-405">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-406">第一個數位的範圍為 2-6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-406">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-407">第九位數是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-407">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-408">十位數是問題位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-408">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-409">第 11 (選擇性) 是個別數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-409">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-410">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-410">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-411">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-411">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-412">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-412">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-413">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-413">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-414">函數函數Func_australian_medical_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-414">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-415">系統找到Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-415">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-416">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-416">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-417">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-417">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_australia_medical_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-418">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-418">Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-419">銀行帳戶詳細資料</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-419">bank account details</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-420">已扣款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-420">medicare payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-421">貸款帳戶</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-421">mortgage account</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-422">銀行付款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-422">bank payments</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-423">資訊分支</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-423">information branch</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-424">信用卡貸款</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-424">credit card loan</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-425">人力服務部門</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-425">department of human services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-426">當地服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-426">local service</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-427">醫療</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-427">medicare</span></span>

   
## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-428">澳洲護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-428">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-429">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-429">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-430">字母后面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-430">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-431">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-431">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-432">字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-432">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-433">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-433">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-434">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-434">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-435">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-435">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-436">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-436">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-437">正則運算式會Regex_australia_passport_number模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-437">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-438">系統找到Keyword_passport或Keyword_australia_passport_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-438">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-439">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-439">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-472">澳大利亞稅務檔案編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-472">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-473">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-474">八到九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-474">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-475">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-476">8 到 9 位數通常以空格表示，如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-476">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-477">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-477">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-478">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-478">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-479">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-479">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-480">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-480">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-481">最後一個數位是檢查數位的 2 到 3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-481">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-482">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-482">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-483">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-483">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-484">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-485">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-485">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-486">函數函數Func_australian_tax_file_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-486">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-487">找不到來自Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number或Keyword_number_exclusions關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-487">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-488">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-488">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-500">奧地利駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-500">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-501">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-502">不含空格和分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-502">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-503">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-503">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-504">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-504">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-505">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-505">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-506">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-506">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-507">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-507">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-508">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-508">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-509">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-509">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-510">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-510">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-637">奧地利身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-637">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-638">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-638">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-639">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-639">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-640">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-640">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-641">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-641">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-642">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-642">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-643">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-643">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-644">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-645">字母、數位和特殊字元的 24 個字元組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-645">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-646">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-647">24 個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-647">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="4056e-648">22 個字母 (不區分大小寫) 數位、數位、反斜線、斜線或加號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-648">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-649">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 數位、數位、反斜線、斜線、加號或等號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-649">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-650">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-651">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-651">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-652">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-653">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-653">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-654">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-654">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-655">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-655">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-656">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-656">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-657">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-657">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-660">personalaus您用 österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-660">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-661">奧地利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-661">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-662">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-663">一個字母，後面接著一個選擇性空格和七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-663">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-664">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-665">一個字母、七位數和一個空格的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-665">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-666">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-666">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-667">一個空格 (選填) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-667">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-668">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-668">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-669">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-669">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-670">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-670">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-671">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-671">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-672">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-672">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-673">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-673">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-674">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-674">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-675">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-675">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-676">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-676">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-677">正則運算式會  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-677">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-678">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-678">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">

          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">

            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />

        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-699">奧地利社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-699">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-700">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-701">指定格式的 10 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-701">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-702">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-703">10 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-703">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-704">對應至序號的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-704">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-705">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-705">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-706">這是對應到 DD一Y (的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-706">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-707">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-707">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-708">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-708">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-709">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-709">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-710">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-710">A DLP policy is has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-711">此函數  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-711">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-712">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-712">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-713">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-713">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-714">此函數  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-714">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-740">奧地利稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-740">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-741">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-742">九位數及選擇性的連字號和斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-742">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-743">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-744">九位數以及選擇性的連字號和斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-744">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-745">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-745">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-746">連字號或 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-746">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-747">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-747">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-748">斜線 (選填) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-748">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-749">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-749">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-750">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-750">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-751">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-751">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-752">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-752">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-753">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-753">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-754">此函數  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-754">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-755">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-755">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-756">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-756">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-757">此函數  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-757">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-780">奧地利的加值稅</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-780">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-781">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-781">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-782">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-782">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-783">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-783">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-784">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-784">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-785">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-785">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-786">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-786">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-787">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-787">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-788">11 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-788">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-789">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-789">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-790">11 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-790">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-792">T 或 t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-792">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-793">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-793">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-794">U 或 u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-794">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-795">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-795">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-796">兩位數或三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-796">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-797">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-797">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-798">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-798">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-799">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-799">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-800">一或兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-800">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-801">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-802">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-802">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-803">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-804">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-804">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-805">函數函數Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-805">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-806">系統找到Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-806">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-807">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-808">函數函數Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-808">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-826">Azure DocumentDB 驗證金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-826">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-827">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-827">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-828">字串 "DocumentDb"，後面接著下圖中概述的字元和字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-828">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-829">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-829">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-830">字串 "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-830">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-831">3-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-831">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-832">大於符號 (>) 、等號 (=) 、引號 (") 或單引號 (') </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-832">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-833">由 86 個小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-833">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-834">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-834">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-835">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-835">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-836">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-836">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-837">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-837">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-838">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-838">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-839">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-839">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-840">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-840">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-855">Azure KMS 資料庫連接字串和 Azure SQL 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-855">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-856">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-856">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-857">字串 "Server"、"server" 或 "data source"，後面接著下面模式所述的字元和字串，包括字串 "cloudapp.azure"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-857">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-858">com" 或 "cloudapp.azure"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-858">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-859">net" 或 "database.windows"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-859">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-860">net"，以及字串 "Password" 或 "password" 或 "pwd"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-860">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-861">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-861">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-862">字串 "Server"、"server" 或 "資料來源"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-862">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-863">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-863">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-864">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-864">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-865">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-865">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-866">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-866">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-867">字串 "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-867">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-868">com"， "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-868">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-869">net" 或 "database.windows"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-869">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-870">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-870">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-871">1-300 個小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-871">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-872">字串 "Password"、"password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-872">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-873">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-873">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-874">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-874">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-875">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-875">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-876">一或多個不是分號 (;) 、引號 (") 或單引號 (') </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-876">one or more characters that is not a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-877">分號 (;) 、引號 (") 或單引號 (') </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-877">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-878">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-878">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-879">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-879">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-880">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-880">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-881">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-881">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-882">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-882">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-883">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-883">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-898">Azure IoT 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-898">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-899">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-900">字串 "HostName"，後面接著下圖中概述的字元和字串，包括字串 "azure-devices。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-900">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-901">net" 和 "SharedAccessKey"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-901">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-902">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-902">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-903">字串 "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-903">the string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-904">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-904">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-905">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-905">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-906">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-906">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-907">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-907">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-908">字串 "azure-devices"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-908">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-909">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-909">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-910">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-910">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-911">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-911">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-912">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-912">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-913">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-913">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-914">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-914">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-915">由 43 個小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-915">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-916">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-916">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-917">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-917">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-918">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-918">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-919">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-919">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-920">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-920">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-921">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-921">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-922">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-922">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-968">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-968">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-969">字串 "redis.cache.windows"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-969">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-970">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-970">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-971">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-971">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-972">字串 "password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-972">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-974">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-974">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-975">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-975">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-976">由 43 個字元組成的任何組合，包括小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-976">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-977">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-977">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-978">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-979">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-979">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-980">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-981">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-981">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-982">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-982">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>


- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1003">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1003">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
