- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1005">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1005">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1006">任何由 43-53 個字元到小寫或大寫字母、位數或百分比符號的組合 (%) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1006">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1007">字串 "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1007">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1008">非小寫或大寫字母、數位或百分比符號的任何字元 (%) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1008">any character that is not a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1009">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1009">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1010">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1010">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1011">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1011">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1012">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1012">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1013">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureSAS找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1013">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1014">Azure 服務行連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1014">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1015">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1016">字串 "EndPoint"，後面接著下圖中概述的字元和字串，包括字串 "servicebus.windows"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1016">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1017">net" 和 "SharedAccesKey"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1017">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1018">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1018">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1019">字串 "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1019">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1020">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1020">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1021">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1021">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1022">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1022">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1023">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1023">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1024">字串 "servicebus.windows"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1024">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1025">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1025">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1026">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1026">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1027">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1027">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1028">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1028">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1029">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1029">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1030">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1030">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1031">由 43 個字元組成的任何組合，包括小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1031">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1032">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1032">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1033">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1033">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1034">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1034">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1035">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1035">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1036">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1036">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1037">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1037">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1038">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1038">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1053">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1053">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1054">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1054">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1055">字串 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"，後面接著下圖中概述的字元和字串，包括字串 "AccountKey"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1055">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1056">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1056">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1057">字串 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1057">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1058">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1058">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1059">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1059">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1060">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1060">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1061">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1061">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1062">字串 "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1062">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1063">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1063">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1064">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1064">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1065">0 到 2 個空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1066">由 86 個字元組成的任何組合，包括小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1066">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1067">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1067">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1068">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1069">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1069">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1070">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1071">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1072">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1072">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1073">正則運算式 **CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1073">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1074">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1074">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1092">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰 (一般) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1092">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1093">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1093">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1094">由 86 個英文小寫或大寫字母、數位、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) 的任何組合，前面或後面接著下列模式所概述的字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1094">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1095">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1095">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1096">零到大於符號 (>) 、單引號 (') 、等號 (=) 、引號 (") 或數位記號 (#) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1096">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1097">由 86 個字元組合成小寫或大寫字母、位數、斜線 (/) 或加號 (+) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1097">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1098">兩個等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1098">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1099">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1099">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1100">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1100">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1101">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1101">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1102">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1102">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1103">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1103">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1104">比利時駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1104">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1105">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1105">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1106">不含空格和分隔符號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1106">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1107">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1107">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1108">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1108">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1109">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1109">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1110">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1110">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1111">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1111">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1112">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1112">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1113">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1113">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1114">關鍵字來自 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1114">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1247">比利時國號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1247">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1248">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1248">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1249">11 位數加上選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1249">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1250">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1250">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1251">11 位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1251">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1252">格式為 YY 的六位數和兩個選擇性的句號。MM.DD生日的輸入</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1252">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1253">點、虛線、空格的選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1253">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1254">三個連續數位 (偶數時為奇數，即使是女性) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1254">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1255">點、虛線、空格的選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1255">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1256">兩個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1256">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1257">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1257">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1258">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1258">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1259">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1259">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1260">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1260">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1261">函數函數Func_belgium_national_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1261">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1262">系統找到Keyword_belgium_national_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1262">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1263">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1263">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1264">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1264">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1265">函數函數Func_belgium_national_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1265">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1266">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1266">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1325">比利時護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1325">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1326">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1326">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1327">兩個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1327">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1328">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1328">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1329">兩個字母，後面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1329">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1330">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1330">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1331">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1331">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1332">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1332">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1333">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1333">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1334">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1334">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1335">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1335">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1336">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` 尋找 DD MM YY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 或找到 `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1336">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1337">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1337">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1338">正則運算式會  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1338">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1339">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1339">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1363">比利時加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1363">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1364">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1364">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1365">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1365">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1366">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1366">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1367">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1367">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1368">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1368">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1369">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1369">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1370">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1370">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1371">12 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1371">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1372">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1372">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1373">12 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1373">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1374">字母 B 或 b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1374">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1375">字母 E 或 e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1375">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1376">一位數 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1376">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1377">從 1 到 9 的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1377">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1378">選擇性的點、連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1378">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1379">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1379">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1380">選擇性的點、連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1380">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1381">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1381">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1382">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1383">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1383">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1384">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1385">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1385">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1386">函數函數Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1386">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1387">系統找到Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1387">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1388">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1388">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1389">函數函數Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1389">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1401">巴西 CPF 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1401">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1402">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1403">11 位數，包含一個檢查數位，而且可以格式化為未格式化</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1403">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1404">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1405">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1405">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1406">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1406">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1407">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1407">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1408">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1408">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1409">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1409">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1410">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1410">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1411">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1411">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1412">兩位數是檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1412">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1413">未格式化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1413">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1414">後兩位數是檢查位數的 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1414">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1415">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1416">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1416">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1417">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1418">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1418">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1419">函數函數Func_brazil_cpf找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1419">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1420">系統找到Keyword_brazil_cpf關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1420">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1421">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1421">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1422">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1422">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1423">函數函數Func_brazil_cpf找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1423">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1424">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1424">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1436">巴西法律實體編號 (CNPJ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1436">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1437">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1438">14 位數，包含註冊號碼、分支號碼和檢查數位，以及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1438">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1439">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1440">14 位數，加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1440">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1441">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1441">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1442">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1442">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1443">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1443">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1444">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1444">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1445">前八 (的三位數是註冊號碼) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1445">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1446">斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1446">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1447">四位數分支號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1447">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1448">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1448">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1449">兩位數是檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1449">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1450">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1450">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1451">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1451">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1452">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1452">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1453">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1453">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1454">函數函數Func_brazil_cnpj找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1454">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1455">系統找到Keyword_brazil_cnpj關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1455">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1456">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1456">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1457">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1457">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1458">函數函數Func_brazil_cnpj找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1458">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1459">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1459">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1481">巴西國家識別卡 (RG) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1481">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1482">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1482">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1483">Registro 提供九位數 (格式) ：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1483">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1484">Registro de Identidade (RIC)  (格式) ：11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1484">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1485">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1485">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1486">Registro 提供 (格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1486">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1487">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1487">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1488">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1488">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1489">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1489">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1490">a period</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1490">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1491">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1491">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1492">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1492">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1493">一位數是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1493">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1494">Registro de Identidade (RIC)  (格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1494">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1495">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1495">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1496">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1496">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1497">一位數是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1497">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1498">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1498">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1499">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1499">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1500">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1500">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1501">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1501">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1502">函數函數Func_brazil_rg找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1502">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1503">系統找到Keyword_brazil_rg關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1503">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1504">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1504">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1505">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1505">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1506">函數函數Func_brazil_rg找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1506">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1507">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1507">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
<Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1510">Cédula de identidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1510">Cédula de identidade</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1512">國名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1512">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1513">número de rreútro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1513">número de rregistro</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1518">保加利亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1518">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1519">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1519">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1520">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1520">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1521">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1521">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1522">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1522">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1523">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1523">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1524">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1524">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1525">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1525">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1526">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1526">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1527">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1527">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1528">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1528">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1655">保加利亞統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1655">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1656">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1656">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1657">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1657">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1658">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1658">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1659">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1659">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1660">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1660">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1661">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1661">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1662">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1663">不含空格和分隔符號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1663">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1664">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1665">不含空格和分隔符號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1665">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1666">對應至 YYMMDD (的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1666">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1667">對應到出生日期的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1667">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1668">對應到性別的一位數：男性的偶數和女性的奇數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1668">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1669">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1669">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1670">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1670">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1671">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1671">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1672">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1672">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1673">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1673">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1674">此函數  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1674">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1675">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1675">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1676">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1676">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1677">此函數  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1677">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1722">保加利亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1722">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1723">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1724">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1724">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1725">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1726">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1726">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1727">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1728">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1728">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1729">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1730">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1730">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1731">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1731">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1732">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1732">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1733">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1733">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1734">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1734">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1735">正則運算式會  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1735">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1736">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1736">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1756">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1756">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1757">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1757">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1758">7 位數或 12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1758">seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1759">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1759">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1760">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼為七位數或十二位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1760">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1761">加拿大銀行帳戶轉場號碼為：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1761">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1762">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1762">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1763">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1763">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1764">三位數 OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1764">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1765">零 "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1765">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1766">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1766">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1767">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1768">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1768">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1769">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1770">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1770">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1771">正則運算式會Regex_canada_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1771">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1772">系統找到Keyword_canada_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1772">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1773">正則運算式會Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1773">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1774">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1774">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1775">正則運算式會Regex_canada_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1775">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1776">系統找到Keyword_canada_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1776">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1777">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1777">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1784">法律代表</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1784">legal representative</span></span>

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1800">加拿大駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1800">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1801">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1801">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1802">因省/市而異</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1802">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1803">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1803">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1804">各種圖樣涵蓋埃布達、英屬哥倫比亞、曼尼托巴、新伯倫多、紐芬蘭/拉拉多文、新聖科提亞、安地卡、布吉納法索、魁北克及哈克圖萬</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1804">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1805">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1806">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1806">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1807">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1808">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1808">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1809">函數 Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1809">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1810">系統找到 Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1810">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1811">系統找到Keyword_canada_drivers_license關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1811">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1947">加拿大健康服務編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1947">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1948">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1949">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1949">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1950">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1951">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1951">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1952">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1952">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1953">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1953">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1954">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1954">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1955">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1955">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1956">正則運算式會Regex_canada_health_service_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1956">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1957">系統找到Keyword_canada_health_service_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1957">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1958">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1958">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_health_service_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1959">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1959">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1960">個人健康號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1960">personal health number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1961">病患資訊</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1961">patient information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1962">健康服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1962">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1963">特殊服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1963">speciality services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1964">汽車意外</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1964">automobile accident</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1965">病患醫院</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1965">patient hospital</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1966">心理醫生</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1966">psychiatrist</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1967">工作者補償</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1967">workers compensation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1968">殘疾</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1968">disability</span></span>

      
## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1969">加拿大護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1969">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1970">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1970">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1971">兩個大寫字母，後面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1971">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1972">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1973">兩個大寫字母，後面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1973">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1974">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1974">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1975">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1975">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-1976">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1976">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-1977">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1977">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1978">正則運算式會Regex_canada_passport_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1978">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-1979">系統找到Keyword_canada_passport_number或Keyword_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-1979">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2009">加拿大個人健康識別號碼 (PHIN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2009">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2010">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2010">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2011">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2011">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2012">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2012">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2013">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2013">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2014">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2015">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2015">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2016">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2017">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2017">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2018">正則運算式會Regex_canada_phin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2018">The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2019">系統至少找到兩Keyword_canada_phin或Keyword_canada_provinces關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2019">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2052">加拿大社會保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2052">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2053">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2054">九位數以及選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2054">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2055">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2055">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2056">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2056">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2057">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2057">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2058">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2058">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2059">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2059">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2060">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2060">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2061">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2061">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2062">未格式化：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2062">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2063">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2063">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2064">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2064">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2065">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2065">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2066">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2066">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2067">函數函數Func_canadian_sin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2067">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2068">至少兩者的任意組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2068">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2069">系統找到Keyword_sin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2069">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2070">系統找到Keyword_sin_collaborative關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2070">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2071">函數Func_eu_date尋找正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2071">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2072">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2072">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2073">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2073">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2074">函數函數Func_unformatted_canadian_sin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2074">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2075">系統找到Keyword_sin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2075">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2076">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2076">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
