## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2101">智利身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2101">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2102">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2102">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2103">七到八位數加上分隔符號以檢查數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2103">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2104">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2104">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2105">七到八位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2105">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2106">一到兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2106">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2107">選擇性期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2107">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2108">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2108">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2109">選擇性期間</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2109">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2110">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2110">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2111">破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2111">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2112">一位數或一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 這是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2112">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2113">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2113">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2114">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2114">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2115">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2115">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2116">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2116">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2117">函數函數Func_chile_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2117">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2118">系統找到Keyword_chile_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2118">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2119">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2119">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2120">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2120">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2121">函數函數Func_chile_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2121">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2122">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2122">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2123">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2123">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2125">cédula de identidad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2125">cédula de identidad</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2126">identificación</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2126">identificación</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2127">國家識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2127">national identification</span></span>

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2159">中國居民身分證 (中國) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2159">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2160">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2160">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2161">18 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2161">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2162">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2162">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2163">18 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2163">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2164">六位數是一個位址代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2164">six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2165">YYYYMMDD 表單中的八位數，這是生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2165">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2166">三位數即為訂單代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2166">three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2167">一位數是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2167">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2168">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2168">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2169">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2169">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2170">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2170">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2171">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2171">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2172">函數函數Func_china_resident_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2172">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2173">系統找到Keyword_china_resident_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2173">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2174">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2174">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2175">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2176">函數函數Func_china_resident_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2176">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2177">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2177">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2178">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2178">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="keyword_china_resident_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2179">Keyword_china_resident_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2179">Keyword_china_resident_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2180">居住身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2180">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2181">中國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2181">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2182">國家識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2182">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2183">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2183">身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2184">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2184">居民 身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2185">居民身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2185">居民身份证</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2186">鑒定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2186">鉴定</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2187">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2187">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2188">居民 身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2188">居民 身份證</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2189">鑑定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2189">鑑定</span></span> 

   
## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2190">信用卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2190">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2191">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2191">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2192">可格式化或未格式化的 14 到 16 位數 (ddddd) 且必須通過 Luhn 檢定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2192">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2193">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2193">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2194">非常複雜且強大的模式可偵測全球所有主要品牌卡片，包括 Visa、MasterCard、Discover Card、JCB、American Express、禮品卡和快閃卡。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2194">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2195">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2195">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2196">是，Luhn 檢查程式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2196">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2197">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2197">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2198">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2198">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2199">此函數Func_credit_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2199">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2200">下列其中一個條件成立：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2200">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2201">系統找到Keyword_cc_verification關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2201">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2202">系統找到Keyword_cc_name關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2202">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2203">函數Func_expiration_date尋找正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2203">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2204">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2204">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2205">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2205">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2206">此函數Func_credit_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2206">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2207">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2207">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2467">克羅地卡駕照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2467">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2468">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2468">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2469">不含空格和分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2469">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2470">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2470">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2471">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2471">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2472">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2472">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2473">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2473">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2474">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2474">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2475">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2475">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2476">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2476">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2477">關鍵字來自 `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2477">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2601">克羅地亞身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2601">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2602">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在歐盟國家識別號碼敏感性資訊類型中，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2602">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2603">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2604">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2604">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2605">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2606">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2606">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2607">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2608">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2608">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2609">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2610">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2611">函數函數Func_croatia_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2611">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2612">系統找到Keyword_croatia_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2612">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2643">克羅地亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2643">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2644">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2645">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2645">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2646">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2647">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2647">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2648">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2648">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2649">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2649">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2650">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2650">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2651">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2651">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2652">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2652">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2653">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2653">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2654">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2654">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2655">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2656">正則運算式會  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2656">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2657">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2657">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2658">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2658">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2662">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2662">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2663">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2663">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2664">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2664">passportno</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2670">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2670">Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2671">將j putov以</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2671">broj putovnice</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2672">Br。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2672">br.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2673">Putov一</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2673">Putovnice</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2675">克羅尼西亞 (OIB) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2675">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2676">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2676">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2677">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2677">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2678">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2678">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2679">11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2679">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2680">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2680">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2681">最後一個數位是一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2681">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2682">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2682">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2683">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2683">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2684">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2684">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2685">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2685">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2686">函數函數Func_croatia_oib_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2686">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2687">系統找到Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2687">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2688">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2688">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2689">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2689">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2690">函數函數Func_croatia_oib_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2690">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2691">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2691">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2722">駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2722">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2723">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2724">不含空格和分隔符號的 12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2724">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2725">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2726">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2726">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2727">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2728">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2728">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2729">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2730">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2730">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2731">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2731">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2732">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2732">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2862">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2862">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2863">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2863">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2864">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2865">不含空格和分隔符號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2865">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2866">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2867">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2867">ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2868">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2868">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2869">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2869">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2870">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2870">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2871">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2871">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2872">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2872">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2873">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2873">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2882">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2882">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2883">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2883">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2884">一個字母，後面接著 6 到 8 位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2884">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2885">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2885">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2886">一個字母后面接著六到八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2886">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2887">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2887">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2888">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2888">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2889">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2889">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2890">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2890">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2891">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2891">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2892">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2892">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2893">正則運算式會 `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` 尋找 DD/MM/YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2893">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2894">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2894">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2895">正則運算式會  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2895">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2896">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2896">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2925">賽普勒斯稅務識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2925">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2926">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2926">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2927">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2927">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2928">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2928">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2929">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2929">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2930">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2930">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2931">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2931">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2932">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2932">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2933">指定模式中八位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2933">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2934">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2934">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2935">八位數和一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2935">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2936">"0" 或 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2936">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2937">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2937">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2938">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2938">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2939">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2939">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2940">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2940">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2941">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2941">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2942">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2942">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2943">此函數  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2943">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2944">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2944">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2945">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2945">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2946">此函數  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2946">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2947">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2947">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2948">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2948">Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2974">捷克駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2974">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2975">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2976">兩個字母后面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2976">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2977">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2978">8 個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2978">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2979">字母 'E' (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2979">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2980">一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2980">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2981">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2981">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2982">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2982">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2983">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2984">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2984">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-2985">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-2986">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2987">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2987">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-2988">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-2988">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3114">捷克文護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3114">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3115">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3115">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3116">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3116">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3117">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3117">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3118">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3118">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3119">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3119">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3120">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3120">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3121">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3122">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3122">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3123">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3123">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3124">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3124">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3125">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3125">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3126">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3126">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3127">正則運算式會  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3127">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3128">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3128">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3150">捷克文個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3150">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3151">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3151">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3152">九位數以及選擇性斜線 (舊格式) 十位數，以及新的格式 (斜線) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3152">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) ten digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3153">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3153">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3154">使用九位數 (舊格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3154">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3155">代表生日的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3155">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3156">選擇性的斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3156">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3157">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3157">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3158">使用新的 (格式的十) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3158">ten digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3159">代表生日的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3159">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3160">選擇性的斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3160">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3161">最後一個數位是檢查數位的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3161">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3162">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3162">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3163">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3163">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3164">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3164">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3165">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3165">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3166">函數函數Func_czech_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3166">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3167">系統找到Keyword_czech_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3167">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3168">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3168">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3169">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3169">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3170">函數函數Func_czech_id_card_new_format找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3170">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3171">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3171">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3218">丹麥駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3218">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3219">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3219">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3220">不含空格和分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3220">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3221">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3221">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3222">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3222">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3223">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3223">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3224">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3224">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3225">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3225">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3226">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3227">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3227">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3228">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3228">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3352">丹麥護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3352">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3353">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3354">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3354">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3355">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3356">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3356">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3357">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3357">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3358">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3358">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3359">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3359">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3360">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3360">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3361">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3361">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3362">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3362">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3363">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date2` 尋找 DD MM YY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3363">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3364">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3364">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3365">正則運算式會  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3365">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3366">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3366">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3386">丹麥個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3386">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3387">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3388">包含連字號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3388">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3389">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3390">十位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3390">ten digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3391">格式 DD您用 6 位數表示生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3391">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3392">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3392">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3393">最後一個數位是檢查數位的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3393">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3394">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3395">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3395">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3396">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3397">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3398">正則運算式會Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3398">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3399">系統找到Keyword_denmark_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3399">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3400">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3400">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3401">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3401">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3402">正則運算式會Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3402">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3403">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3403">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3475">國家調查 (安全) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3475">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3476">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3476">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3477">兩個字母后面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3477">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3478">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3478">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3479">模式必須包含下列所有專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3479">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3480">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 一組可能字母：abcdefghjklmnprstux，這是一個註冊表代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3480">one letter (not case sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3481">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) ，即為報名者姓氏或數位 '9' 的第一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3481">one letter (not case sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3482">7 位數，最後一位是檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3482">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3483">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3483">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3484">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3484">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3485">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3485">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3486">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3486">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3487">函數函數Func_dea_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3487">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3488">找到 `Keyword_dea_number` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3488">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3489">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3489">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3490">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3490">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3491">函數函數Func_dea_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3491">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3492">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3492">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3493">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3493">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3494">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3494">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3495">Dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3495">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3496">Dea#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3496">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3497">稅務強制執行系統</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3497">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3498">政策強制執行機關</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3498">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3499">愛沙尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3499">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3500">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3500">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3501">兩個字母后面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3501">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3502">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3503">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3503">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3504">字母 "ET" (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3504">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3505">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3505">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3506">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3507">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3507">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3508">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3509">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3509">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3510">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3510">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3511">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3511">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3637">愛沙尼亞個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3637">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3638">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3638">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3639">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3639">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3640">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3640">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3641">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3641">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3642">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3642">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3643">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3643">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3644">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3645">不含空格和分隔符號的 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3645">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3646">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3647">11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3647">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3648">一位數，對應到性別和一世紀 (奇數男性，偶數女性;1-2：19 世紀;3-4：20 世紀;5-6：21 世紀) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3648">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3649">對應至 YYMMDD (生日的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3649">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3650">對應至相同日期的序列值分隔人的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3650">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3651">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3651">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3652">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3653">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3653">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3654">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3655">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3655">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3656">此函數  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3656">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3657">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3657">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3658">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3658">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3659">此函數  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3659">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
