## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3692">愛沙尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3692">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3693">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3694">一個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3694">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3695">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3696">一個字母后面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3696">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3697">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3697">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3698">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3698">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3699">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3699">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3700">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3700">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3701">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3701">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3702">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3702">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3703">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3703">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3704">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3704">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3705">正則運算式會  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3705">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3706">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3706">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3724">歐盟轉帳卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3724">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3725">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3725">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3726">16 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3726">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3727">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3727">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3728">非常複雜且強大的模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3728">Very complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3729">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3730">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3730">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-3731">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-3732">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3732">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3733">函數函數Func_eu_debit_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3733">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3734">至少下列其中一個條件成立：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3734">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3735">系統找到Keyword_eu_debit_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3735">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3736">系統找到Keyword_card_terms_dict關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3736">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3737">系統找到Keyword_card_security_terms_dict關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3737">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3738">系統找到Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3738">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3739">函數Func_expiration_date尋找正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3739">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-3740">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-3740">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4186">芬蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4186">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4187">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4188">包含連字號的十位數和字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4188">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4189">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4190">包含連字號的十位數和字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4190">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4191">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4191">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4192">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4192">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4193">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4193">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4194">數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4194">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4195">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4195">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4196">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4196">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4197">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4197">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4198">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4198">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4199">正則運算式會  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4199">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4200">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4200">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4331">芬蘭歐洲健康保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4331">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4332">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4332">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4333">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4333">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4334">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4334">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4335">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4335">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4336">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4336">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4337">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4337">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4338">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4338">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4339">20 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4339">20 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4340">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4340">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4341">20 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4341">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4342">十位數 - 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4342">ten digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4343">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4343">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4344">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4344">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4345">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4345">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4346">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4346">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4347">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4347">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4348">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4348">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4349">RegEx 索引Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4349">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4350">系統找到Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4350">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4368">芬蘭國識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4368">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4369">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4369">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4370">六位數加上一個字元，表示一世紀加上三位數加上一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4370">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4371">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4371">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4372">模式必須包含下列所有專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4372">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4373">格式 DD有 6 位數是生日的 DD一</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4373">six digits in the format format DDMMYY which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4374">century 標記 ('-'、'+' 或 'a') </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4374">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4375">三位數個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4375">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4376">這是一個 (大小寫不區分) 數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4376">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4377">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4378">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4378">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4379">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4380">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4380">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4381">函數函數Func_finnish_national_id尋找符合模式的內容</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4381">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4382">找到您Keyword_finnish_national_id關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4382">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4383">檢查和傳遞</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4383">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4384">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4384">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4385">函數函數Func_finnish_national_id尋找符合模式的內容</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4385">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4386">檢查和傳遞</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4386">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4435">芬蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4435">Finland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4436">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4436">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4437">九個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4437">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4438">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4438">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4439">九個字母和數位的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4439">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4440">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4440">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4441">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4441">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4442">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4443">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4443">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4444">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4445">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4445">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4446">正則運算式會Regex_finland_passport_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4446">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4447">系統找到Keywords_eu_passport_number_common或Keyword_finland_passport_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4447">A keyword from Keywords_eu_passport_number_common or Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4468">法國駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4468">France driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4469">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4470">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4470">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4471">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4472">12 位數與驗證以折扣類似模式 ，例如法文電話號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4472">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4473">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4474">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4474">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4475">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4476">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4476">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4477">函數函數Func_french_drivers_license找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4477">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4478">找到您Keyword_french_drivers_license關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4478">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4605">法國健康保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4605">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4606">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4606">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4607">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4607">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4608">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4608">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4609">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4609">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4610">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4610">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4611">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4611">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4612">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4612">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4613">21 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4613">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4614">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4614">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4615">21 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4615">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4616">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4616">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4617">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4617">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4618">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4618">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4619">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4619">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4620">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4620">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4621">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4621">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4622">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4622">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4623">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4623">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4624">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4624">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4625">RegEx Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4625">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4626">找到您Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4626">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4627">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4627">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4628">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4628">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4629">保險卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4629">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4630">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4630">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4631">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4631">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4632">法國國家/ (資訊) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4632">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4633">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4633">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4634">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4634">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4635">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4635">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4636">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4636">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4637">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4637">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4638">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4638">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4639">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4639">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4640">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4640">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4641">正則運算式會Regex_france_cni找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4641">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4642">系統找到Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4642">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4648">Cni#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4648">cni#</span></span>

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4656">法國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4656">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4657">此敏感性資訊類型實體可在歐盟護照號碼敏感性資訊類型中提供，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4657">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4658">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4659">九位數和字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4659">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4660">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4661">九位數和字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4661">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4662">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4662">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4663">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4663">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4664">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4664">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4665">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4665">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4666">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4666">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4667">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4667">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4668">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4668">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4669">函數函數Func_fr_passport找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4669">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4670">系統找到Keyword_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4670">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4691">INSEE 中 (或) 的法國社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4691">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4692">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在歐盟社會安全號碼與同等識別碼敏感性資訊類型中，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4692">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4693">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4694">15 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4694">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4695">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4696">必須符合兩種模式其中之一：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4696">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4697">13 位數，後接空格後接兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4697">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4698">或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4698">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4699">連續 15 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4699">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4700">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4700">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4701">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4701">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4702">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4702">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4703">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，95% 都表示已偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4703">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4704">函數會Func_french_insee或Func_fr_insee尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4704">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4705">系統找到Keyword_fr_insee關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4705">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4706">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4706">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4707">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4707">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4708">函數會Func_french_insee或Func_fr_insee尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4708">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4709">找不到來自Keyword_fr_insee關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4709">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4710">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4710">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4736">法國稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4736">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4737">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4738">13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4738">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4739">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4740">13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4740">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4741">一位數，必須是 0、1、2 或 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4741">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4742">1 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4742">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4743">空格 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4743">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4744">2 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4744">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4745">空格 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4745">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4746">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4746">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4747">空格 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4747">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4748">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4748">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4749">空格 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4749">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4750">3 個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4750">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4751">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4751">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4752">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4752">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4753">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4753">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4754">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4754">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4755">此函數  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4755">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4756">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4756">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4757">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4757">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4758">此函數  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4758">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4778">法國加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4778">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4779">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4779">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4780">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4780">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4781">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4781">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4782">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4782">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4783">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4783">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4784">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4784">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4785">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4785">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4786">13 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4786">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4787">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4787">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4788">13 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4788">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4789">兩個字母 - FR (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4789">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4790">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4790">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4791">兩個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4791">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4792">選擇性空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4792">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4793">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4793">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4794">選擇性空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4794">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4795">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4795">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4796">選擇性空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4796">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4797">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4797">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4798">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4799">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4799">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4800">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4801">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4801">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4802">函數函數Func_france_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4802">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4803">系統找到Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4803">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4804">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4804">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4805">函數函數Func_france_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4805">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4818">德國駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4818">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4819">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4820">11 位數和字母的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4820">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4821">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4822">11 位數和字母 (大小寫不區分) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4822">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4823">數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4823">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4824">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4824">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4825">六位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4825">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4826">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4826">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4827">數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4827">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4828">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4829">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4830">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4831">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4831">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4832">函數函數Func_german_drivers_license找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4832">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4833">系統找到Keyword_german_drivers_license_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4833">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4834">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4834">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4983">德國身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4983">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4984">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4984">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4985">自 2010 年 11 月 1 日起：九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4985">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4986">從 1987 年 4 月 1 日到 2010 年 10 月 31 日：10 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4986">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4987">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4987">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4988">自 2010 年 11 月 1 日起：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4988">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4989">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4989">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4990">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4990">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4991">從 1987 年 4 月 1 日到 2010 年 10 月 31 日：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4991">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4992">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4992">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4993">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4993">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4994">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4994">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4995">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4995">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-4996">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4996">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4997">正則運算式會Regex_germany_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4997">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-4998">系統找到Keyword_germany_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4998">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-4999">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-4999">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5000">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5000">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5001">aus一s</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5001">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5002">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5002">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5003">識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5003">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5004">identifidentation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5004">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5005">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5005">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5006">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5006">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5007">身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5007">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5008">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5008">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5009">個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5009">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5010">personalaus一s</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5010">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5011">persönliche id nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5011">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5012">persönliche identifidentationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5012">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5013">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5013">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5014">德國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5014">Germany passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5015">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5016">十位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5016">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5017">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5018">模式必須包含下列所有專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5018">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5019">第一個字元是這個集合中的數位或字母 (C、F、G、H、J、K) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5019">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5020">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5020">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5021">此集合中的五位數或英文字母 (C、-H、J-N、P、R、T、V-Z) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5021">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5022">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5022">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5023">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5023">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5024">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5024">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5025">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5025">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5026">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5026">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5027">函數函數Func_german_passport找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5027">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5028">關鍵字來自 `Keyword_german_passport` `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5028">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5029">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5029">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5030">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5030">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5031">函數函數Func_german_passport_data找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5031">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5032">關鍵字來自 `Keyword_german_passport` `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5032">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5033">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5033">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5047">護照#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5047">passport #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5049">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5049">passports</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5056">德國稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5056">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5057">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5058">不含空格和分隔符號的 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5058">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5059">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5059">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5060">11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5060">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5061">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5061">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5062">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5062">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5063">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5063">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5064">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5064">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5065">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5065">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5066">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5066">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5067">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5067">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5068">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5068">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5069">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5069">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5070">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5070">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5071">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5071">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5072">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5072">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5073">此函數  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5073">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5074">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5074">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5075">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5075">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5076">此函數  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5076">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5077">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5077">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5078">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5078">Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5079">identifidentationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5079">identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5080">sterer 識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5080">steuer id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5081">ststeridentifidentationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5081">steueridentifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5082">sterernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5082">steuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5083">稅務識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5083">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5084">稅務識別否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5084">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5085">稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5085">tax identification number</span></span>

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5102">德國加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5102">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5103">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5103">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5104">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5104">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5105">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5105">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5106">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5106">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5107">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5107">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5108">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5108">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5109">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5109">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5110">11 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5110">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5111">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5111">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5112">11 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5112">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5113">字母 D 或 d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5113">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5114">字母 E 或 e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5114">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5115">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5115">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5116">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5116">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5117">這是選擇性的空格或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5117">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5118">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5118">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5119">這是選擇性的空格或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5119">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5120">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5120">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5121">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5121">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5122">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5122">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5123">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5123">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5124">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5124">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5125">函數函數Func_germany_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5125">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5126">系統找到Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5126">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5127">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5127">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5128">函數函數Func_germany_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5128">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5131">加值稅 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5131">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5132">加值稅 否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5132">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5133">加值稅#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5133">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5134">vat# mehrwertst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5134">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5138">希臘駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5138">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5139">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5139">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5140">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5140">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5141">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5141">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5142">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5142">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5143">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5143">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5144">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5144">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5145">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5145">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5146">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5146">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5147">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5147">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5148">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5148">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
