## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5274">希臘國識別碼卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5274">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5275">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5276">7-8 個字母和數位的組合加上虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5276">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5277">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5278">七個字母和數位會 (舊格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5278">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5279">一個字母 (希臘字母的任何字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5279">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5280">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5280">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5281">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5281">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5282">八個字母和數位會 (格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5282">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5283">兩個字母大寫字元同時出現在希臘文和拉丁字母 (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5283">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5284">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5284">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5285">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5285">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5286">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5286">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5287">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5287">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5288">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5288">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5289">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5289">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5290">正則運算式會Regex_greece_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5290">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5291">系統找到Keyword_greece_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5291">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5292">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5292">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5293">正則運算式會Regex_greece_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5293">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5294">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5294">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5295">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5295">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5296">希臘文識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5296">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5297">希臘文識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5297">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5298">希臘文個人識別碼卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5298">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5299">希臘文的希臘文識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5299">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5300">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5300">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5301">tautot為</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5301">tautotita</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5302">ταυτότητα</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5302">ταυτότητα</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5303">ταυτότητας</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5303">ταυτότητας</span></span>


## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5304">希臘護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5304">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5305">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5305">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5306">兩個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5306">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5307">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5307">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5308">兩個字母后面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5308">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5309">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5309">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5310">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5310">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5311">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5311">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5312">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5312">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5313">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5313">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5314">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5314">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5315">正則運算式會 `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` 尋找 DD MMM YY 格式 (範例 - 28 Aug 19) 或 `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` 找到關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5315">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5316">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5316">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5317">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5317">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5318">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5318">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5335">希臘社會安全號碼 (AMKA) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5335">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5336">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5336">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5337">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5337">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5338">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5338">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5339">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5339">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5340">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5340">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5341">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5341">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5342">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5342">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5343">不含空格和分隔符號的 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5343">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5344">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5344">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5345">6 位數作為生日 YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5345">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5346">4 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5346">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5347">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5347">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5348">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5348">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5349">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5349">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5350">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5350">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5351">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5351">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5352">此函數  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5352">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5353">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5353">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5354">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5354">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5355">此函數  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5355">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5367">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5367">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5368">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5368">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5369">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5369">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5372">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5372">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5373">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5373">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5374">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5374">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5375">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5375">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5376">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5376">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5377">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5378">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5378">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5379">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5380">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5380">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5381">正則運算式會  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5381">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5382">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5382">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5411">香港身分識別卡 (HKID) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5411">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5412">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5412">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5413">8-9 個字母和數位的組合，再加上最後一個字元的選擇性括弧</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5413">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5414">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5414">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5415">8-9 個字母的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5415">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5416">1 到 2 個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5416">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5417">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5417">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5418">最後一個字元 (數位或字母 A) ，這是檢查數位，可選擇性地用括弧括住。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5418">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5419">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5420">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5420">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5421">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5422">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5422">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5423">函數函數Func_hong_kong_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5423">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5424">系統找到Keyword_hong_kong_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5424">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5425">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5425">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5426">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5426">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5427">函數函數Func_hong_kong_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5427">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5428">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5428">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5468">匈牙利駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5468">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5469">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5470">兩個字母后面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5470">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5471">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5472">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5472">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5473">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5473">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5474">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5474">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5475">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5476">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5476">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5477">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5478">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5478">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5479">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5479">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5480">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5480">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5605">匈牙利個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5605">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5606">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5606">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5607">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5607">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5608">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5608">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5609">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5609">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5610">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5610">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5611">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5611">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5612">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5612">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5613">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5613">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5614">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5614">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5615">11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5615">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5616">一位數對應到性別 (1 小時、2 歲、其他數位也可用於 1900 之前所生，或雙母母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5616">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5617">對應至 YYMMDD (出生日期的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5617">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5618">對應至序號的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5618">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5619">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5619">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5620">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5620">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5621">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5621">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5622">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5622">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5623">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5623">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5624">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5624">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5625">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5625">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5626">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5626">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5627">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5627">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5638">匈牙利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5638">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5639">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5640">兩個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的六位數或七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5640">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5641">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5642">兩個字母后面接著六位數或七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5642">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5643">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5643">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5644">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5644">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5645">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5645">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5646">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5646">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5647">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5647">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5648">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5648">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5649">正則運算式會尋找 `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (範例 - 01 MÁR/MAR 12 格式) 或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5649">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5650">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5650">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5651">正則運算式會  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5651">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5652">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5652">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5669">匈牙利社會安全號碼 (TAJ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5669">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5670">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5670">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5671">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5671">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5672">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5672">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5673">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5673">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5674">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5674">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5675">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5675">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5676">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5676">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5677">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5677">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5678">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5678">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5679">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5679">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5680">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5680">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5681">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5681">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5701">匈牙利稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5701">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5702">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5702">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5703">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5703">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5704">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5704">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5705">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5705">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5706">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5706">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5707">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5707">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5708">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5709">十位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5709">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5710">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5710">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5711">十位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5711">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5712">一位數必須是 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5712">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5713">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5713">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5714">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5714">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5715">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5716">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5716">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5717">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5718">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5718">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5719">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5719">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5720">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5720">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5721">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5721">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5722">此函數  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5722">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5748">匈牙利加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5748">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5749">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5749">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5750">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5750">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5751">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5751">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5752">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5752">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5753">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5753">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5754">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5754">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5755">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5755">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5756">10 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5756">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5757">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5757">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5758">10 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5758">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5759">2 個字母 - HU 或 hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5759">2 letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5760">選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5760">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5761">8 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5761">8 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5762">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5763">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5763">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5764">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5764">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5765">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5765">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5766">函數函數Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5766">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5767">系統找到Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5767">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5768">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5768">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5769">函數函數Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5769">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5783">PAN (的印度永久) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5783">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5784">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5784">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5785">10 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5785">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5786">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5786">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5787">10 個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5787">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5788">三個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5788">Three letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5789">C、P、H、F、A、T、B、L、J、G 中的字母 (區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5789">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5790">一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5790">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5791">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5791">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5792">字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5792">A letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5793">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5793">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5794">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5794">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5795">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5795">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5796">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5796">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5797">正則運算式會Regex_india_permanent_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5797">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5798">系統找到Keyword_india_permanent_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5798">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5799">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5799">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5800">正則運算式會Regex_india_permanent_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5800">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5802">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5802">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5805">印度唯一 (Aadhaar) 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5805">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5806">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5807">包含選擇性空格或虛線的 12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5807">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5808">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5809">12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5809">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5810">不是 0 或 1 的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5810">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5811">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5811">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5812">選擇性空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5812">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5813">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5813">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5814">選擇性空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5814">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5815">最後一個數位，即檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5815">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5816">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5816">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5817">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5817">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5818">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5818">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5819">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5819">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5820">函數函數Func_india_aadhaar找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5820">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5821">系統找到Keyword_india_aadhar關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5821">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5822">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5822">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5823">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5823">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5824">函數函數Func_india_aadhaar找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5824">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5825">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5825">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5831">Uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5831">uid</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5834">印尼身分識別卡 (KTP) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5834">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5835">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5835">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5836">包含選擇性句號的 16 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5836">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5837">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5837">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5838">16 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5838">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5839">兩位數的省碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5839">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5840">期間 (選擇性) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5840">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5841">兩位數 regency 或城市代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5841">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5842">兩位數子區碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5842">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5843">期間 (選擇性) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5843">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5844">DD一Y 格式中的六位數是生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5844">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5845">期間 (選擇性) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5845">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5846">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5846">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5847">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5847">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5848">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5848">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5849">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5849">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5850">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5850">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5851">正則運算式會Regex_indonesia_id_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5851">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5852">系統找到Keyword_indonesia_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5852">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5853">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5853">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5854">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5854">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5855">Ktp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5855">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5856">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5856">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5857">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5857">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5858">IBAN (國際) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5858">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5859">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5860">國碼 (兩個字母) 加上 (兩位數) 加上 bban 號碼 (最多 30 個字元) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5860">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5861">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5862">模式必須包含下列所有專案：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5862">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5863">兩個字母的國碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5863">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5864">兩個檢查數位 (後接選擇性空格) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5864">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5865">1 到 7 個包含四個字母或數位的 (，可以使用空格或空格) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5865">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5866">1-3 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5866">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5867">每個國家/地區的格式稍有不同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5867">The format for each country is slightly different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5868">IBAN 敏感性資訊類型涵蓋這 60 個國家/地區：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5868">The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5869">ad， ae， al， at， az， ba， be， bg， bh， ch， cr， cy， kw， de， dk， do， ee， es， fi， fo， fr， gb， ge， gi， gl， gr， hr， hu， ie， il， is， it， kw， kz， lb， li， lt， lu， lv， mc， md， me， mk， mr， mt， mu， nl， no， pl， pt， ro， rs， sa， se， si， sk， sm， tn， tr， vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5869">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5870">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5870">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5871">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5871">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5872">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5872">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5873">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5873">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5874">函數函數Func_iban找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5874">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5875">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5875">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5876">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5876">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5877">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5877">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5878">國際疾病分類 (ICD-10-CM) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5878">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5879">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5879">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5880">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5880">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5881">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5881">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5882">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5882">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5883">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5884">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5884">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5885">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5886">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5886">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5887">系統找到Dictionary_icd_10_updated關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5887">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5888">系統找到Dictionary_icd_10_codes關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5888">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5889">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5889">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5890">系統找到Dictionary_icd_10_更新的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5890">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5891">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5891">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5892">來自 Dictionary_icd_10_updated 關鍵字字典的任何字詞，該字典是以國際預防分類、第十次修訂、 ([ICD-10-CM ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5892">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5893">此類型只會尋找該術語，不會尋找保險代碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5893">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5894">任何來自 Dictionary_icd_10_codes 關鍵字字典的字詞，該字典是以國際預防分類、第十次修訂、 ([ICD-10-CM ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5894">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5895">此類型只會尋找保險代碼，不會尋找描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5895">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5896">國際疾病分類 (ICD-9-CM) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5896">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5897">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5897">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5898">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5898">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5899">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5899">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5900">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5900">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5901">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5901">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5902">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5902">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5903">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5903">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5904">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5904">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5905">系統找到Dictionary_icd_9_updated關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5905">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5906">系統找到Dictionary_icd_9_codes關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5906">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5907">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5907">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5908">系統找到Dictionary_icd_9_updated關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5908">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5909">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5909">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5910">任何來自 Dictionary_icd_9_updated 關鍵字字典的字詞，該字典是以國際醫療分類、第九次修訂、系統 ([ICD-9-CM ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5910">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5911">此類型只會尋找該術語，不會尋找保險代碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5911">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5912">任何來自 Dictionary_icd_9_codes 關鍵字字典的字詞，該字典是以國際醫療分類、第九次修訂、系統 ([ICD-9-CM ](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5912">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5913">此類型只會尋找保險代碼，不會尋找描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5913">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5914">IP 位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5914">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5915">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5915">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5916">IPv4：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5916">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5917">複雜模式，此模式適用于格式化 (期間) 格式 (未格式化的) IPv4 位址版本沒有句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5917">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5918">IPv6：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5918">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5919">將已格式化的 IPv6 數位計算為包含冒號 (複雜模式) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5919">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5920">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5920">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5921">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5921">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5922">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5922">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5923">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5923">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5924">對於 IPv6，DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5924">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5925">正則運算式會Regex_ipv6_address找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5925">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5926">找不到來自Keyword_ipaddress關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5926">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5927">對於 IPv4，DLP 政策在 300 個字元的鄰近範圍內，95% 都確信它可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5927">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5928">正則運算式會Regex_ipv4_address找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5928">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5929">系統找到Keyword_ipaddress關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5929">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5930">對於 IPv6，DLP 政策在 300 個字元的鄰近範圍內，95% 都確信它可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5930">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5931">正則運算式會Regex_ipv6_address找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5931">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5932">找不到來自Keyword_ipaddress關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5932">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5940">愛爾蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5940">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5941">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5941">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5942">六位數後面接著四個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5942">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5943">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5943">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5944">六位數和四個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5944">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5945">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5945">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5946">四個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5946">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5947">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5947">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5948">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5948">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-5949">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5949">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-5950">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5950">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5951">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5951">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-5952">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-5952">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
