## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6076">愛爾蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6076">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6077">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6078">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6078">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6079">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6080">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6080">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6081">兩位數或兩個字母 (大小寫不區分) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6081">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6082">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6082">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6083">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6084">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6084">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6085">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6086">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6086">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6087">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6087">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6088">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6088">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6089">正則運算式會尋找 `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (範例 - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6089">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6090">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6090">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6091">正則運算式會  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6091">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6092">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6092">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6116">愛爾蘭個人公用服務 (PPS) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6116">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6117">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6117">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6118">舊格式會 (2012 年 12 月 31 日) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6118">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6119">七位數，後面接著 1-2 個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6119">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6120">2013 (1 日及之後的新格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6120">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6121">七位數後面接著兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6121">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6122">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6123">舊格式會 (2012 年 12 月 31 日) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6123">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6124">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6124">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6125">一到兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6125">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6126">2013 (1 日及之後的新格式) ：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6126">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6127">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6127">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6128">字母 (不區分大小寫) 這是字母檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6128">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6129">範圍 A-I 或 "W" 的選擇性字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6129">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6130">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6131">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6131">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6132">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6133">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6133">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6134">函數函數Func_ireland_pps找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6134">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6135">系統找到Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6135">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6136">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6136">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6137">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6137">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6138">函數函數Func_ireland_pps找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6138">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6139">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6155">Psp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6155">psp</span></span>

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6184">以色列銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6184">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6185">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6185">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6186">13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6186">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6187">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6187">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6188">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6188">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6189">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6189">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6190">破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6190">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6191">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6191">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6192">破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6192">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6193">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6193">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6194">未格式化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6194">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6195">13 個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6195">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6196">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6197">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6197">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6198">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6199">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6199">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6200">正則運算式會Regex_israel_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6200">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6201">系統找到Keyword_israel_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6201">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6202">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6202">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6203">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6203">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6204">銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6204">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6205">銀行帳戶</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6205">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6206">帳號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6206">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6207">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6207">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6208">以色列國家識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6208">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6209">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6209">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6210">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6210">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6211">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6211">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6212">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6212">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6213">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6213">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6214">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6214">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6215">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6215">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6216">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6216">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6217">函數函數Func_israeli_national_id_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6217">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6218">系統找到Keyword_Israel_National_ID關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6218">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6219">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6219">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6220">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6220">Keywords</span></span>

-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6222">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6222">מספר זהות</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6223">מספר זיה וי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6223">מספר זיה וי</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6224">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6224">מספר זיהוי ישר אלי</span></span>      
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6225">זהותישר אלית</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6225">זהותישר אלית</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6226">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6226">هو ية اسرائيل ية عدد</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6227">هوية إسرائ يلية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6227">هوية إسرائ يلية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6228">رقم الهوية</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6228">رقم الهوية</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6229">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6229">عدد هوية فريدة من نوعها</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6230">idnumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6230">idnumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6231">識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6231">id number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6232">身分識別否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6232">identity no</span></span>        
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6233">identitynumber#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6233">identitynumber#</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6234">身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6234">identity number</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6235">identidentitynumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6235">israeliidentitynumber</span></span>       
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6236">個人識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6236">personal id</span></span>
-   <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6237">唯一識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6237">unique id</span></span>  

   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6238">義大利駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6238">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6239">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6239">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6240">10 個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6240">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6241">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6241">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6242">10 個字母和數位的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6242">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6243">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6243">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6244">字母 "A" 或 "V" (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6244">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6245">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6245">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6246">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6246">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6247">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6248">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6248">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6249">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6250">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6250">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6251">正則運算式會Regex_italy_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6251">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6252">系統找到Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6252">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6253">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6253">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6254">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6254">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6255">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6255">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6256">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6256">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6257">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6257">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6258">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6258">patenti di guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6260">義大利會計代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6260">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6261">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6261">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6262">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6262">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6263">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6263">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6264">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6264">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6265">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6265">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6266">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6266">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6267">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6268">指定模式中 16 個字元的字母和數位組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6268">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6269">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6270">16 個字元的字母和數位組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6270">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6271">三個字母對應到家庭姓名中前三個子音</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6271">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6272">對應到名字中第一個、第三個及第四個子音的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6272">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6273">對應至生日年份最後一位數的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6273">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6274">一個對應到生日月份字母的字母 —字母是按照字母順序排列，但只會使用 A 到 E、H、L、M、P、R 到 T 的字母 (因此，January 是 A，而十月是 R) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6274">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6275">兩位數對應到生日當天，為了區分性別，會為女性在生日加上 40。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6275">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6276">四位數對應到該人員所生之國家 (區碼特定的區碼，適用于其他國家/) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6276">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6277">一個等位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6277">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6278">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6278">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6279">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6279">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6280">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6280">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6281">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6281">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6282">此函數  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6282">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6283">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6283">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6284">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6284">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6285">此函數  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6285">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6320">義大利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6320">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6321">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6321">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6322">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6322">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6323">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6323">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6324">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6324">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6325">兩位數或兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6325">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6326">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6326">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6327">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6327">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6328">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6328">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6329">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6329">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6330">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6330">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6331">正則運算式會  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6331">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6332">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6332">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6333">正則運算式會尋找 `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YYYY (範例 - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) 或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6333">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6334">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6334">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6335">正則運算式會  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6335">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6336">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6336">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6360">義大利加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6360">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6361">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6361">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6362">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6362">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6363">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6363">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6364">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6364">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6365">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6365">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6366">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6366">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6367">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6368">包含選擇性分隔符號的 13 個字元 Alphanumeric 模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6368">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6369">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6370">包含選擇性分隔符號的 13 個字元 Alphanumeric 模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6370">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6371">I 或 i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6371">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6372">T 或 t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6372">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6373">選擇性空格、點、連字號或逗號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6373">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6374">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6374">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6375">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6375">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6376">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6376">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6377">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6377">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6378">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6378">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6379">函數函數Func_italy_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6379">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6380">系統找到Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6380">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6381">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6381">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6382">函數函數Func_italy_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6382">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6390">日本銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6390">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6391">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6391">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6392">7 或 8 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6392">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6393">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6393">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6394">銀行帳戶號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6394">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6395">7 或 8 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6395">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6396">銀行帳戶分支代碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6396">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6397">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6397">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6398">這是選擇性的空格 (虛線) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6398">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6399">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6399">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6400">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6400">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6401">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6401">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6402">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6402">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6403">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6403">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6404">函數函數Func_jp_bank_account找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6404">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6405">系統找到Keyword_jp_bank_account關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6405">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6406">下列其中一個條件成立：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6406">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6407">函數函數Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6407">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6408">系統找到Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6408">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6409">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6409">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6410">函數函數Func_jp_bank_account找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6410">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6411">系統找到Keyword_jp_bank_account關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6411">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6458">日本駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6458">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6459">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6459">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6460">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6460">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6461">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6461">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6462">12 個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6462">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6463">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6464">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6464">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6465">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6466">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6466">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6467">函數函數Func_jp_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6467">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6468">系統找到Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6468">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6469">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6469">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6470">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6470">Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6506">日本我的號碼 - 公司</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6506">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6507">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6507">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6508">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6508">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6509">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6509">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6510">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6510">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6511">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6511">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6512">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6512">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6513">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6514">13 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6514">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6515">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6516">13 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6516">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6517">一位數到九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6517">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6518">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6518">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6519">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6519">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6520">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6520">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6521">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6521">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6522">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6522">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6523">函數函數Func_japanese_my_number_corporate找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6523">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6524">系統找到Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6524">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6525">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6525">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6526">函數函數Func_japanese_my_number_corporate找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6526">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6527">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6527">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6528">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6528">Keyword_japan_my_number_corporate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6529">公司編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6529">corporate number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6531">共通番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6531">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6532">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6532">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6533">マイナンバーカード番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6533">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6534">個人番號カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6534">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6535">個人識別番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6535">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6536">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6536">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6537">法人番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6537">法人番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6538">指定通知書</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6538">指定通知書</span></span>


## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6539">日本我的號碼 - 個人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6539">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6540">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6540">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6541">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6541">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6542">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6542">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6543">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6543">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6544">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6544">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6545">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6545">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6546">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6546">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6547">12 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6547">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6548">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6548">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6549">12 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6549">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6550">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6550">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6551">選擇性空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6551">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6552">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6552">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6553">選擇性空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6553">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6554">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6554">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6555">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6556">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6556">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6557">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6558">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6558">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6559">函數函數Func_japanese_my_number_personal找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6559">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6560">系統找到Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6560">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6561">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6561">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6562">函數函數Func_japanese_my_number_personal找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6562">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6563">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6563">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_japan_my_number_personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6564">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6564">Keyword_japan_my_number_personal</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6565">我的號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6565">my number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6569">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6569">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6570">マイナンバーカード番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6570">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6571">個人番號カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6571">個人番号カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6572">個人識別番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6572">個人識別番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6573">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6573">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6574">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6574">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6575">日本護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6575">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6576">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6576">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6577">兩個字母后面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6577">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6578">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6578">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6579">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6579">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6580">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6580">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6581">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6581">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6582">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6582">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6583">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6583">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6584">函數函數Func_jp_passport找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6584">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6585">系統找到Keyword_jp_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6585">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6586">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6586">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6587">Keyword_jp_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6587">Keyword_jp_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6588">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6588">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6589">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6589">Passport Number</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6602">日本居住卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6602">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6603">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6604">12 個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6604">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6605">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6606">12 個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6606">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6607">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6607">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6608">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6608">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6609">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6609">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6610">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6610">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6611">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6611">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6612">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6612">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6613">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6613">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6614">正則運算式會Regex_jp_residence_card_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6614">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6615">系統找到Keyword_jp_residence_card_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6615">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6616">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6616">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6617">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6617">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6618">居住卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6618">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6619">居住卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6619">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6620">居住卡#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6620">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6621">在留カード番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6621">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6622">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6622">在留カード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6623">在留番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6623">在留番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6624">日本居民註冊號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6624">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6625">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6625">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6626">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6626">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6627">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6627">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6628">連續 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6628">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6629">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6629">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6630">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6630">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6631">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6631">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6632">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6632">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6633">函數函數Func_jp_resident_registration_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6633">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6634">系統找到Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6634">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6635">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6635">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_resident_registration_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6636">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6636">Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6637">居民註冊號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6637">Resident Registration Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6638">居民基本註冊表號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6638">Residents Basic Registry Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6639">居住註冊號碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6639">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6640">住家註冊人否。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6640">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6641">人口基本註冊表否。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6641">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6642">基本居住登記簿否。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6642">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6643">外國人登録証明書番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6643">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6644">証明書番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6644">証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6645">登録番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6645">登録番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6646">外國人登録証</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6646">外国人登録証</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6647">日本社會保險編號 (SIN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6647">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6648">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6648">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6649">7-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6649">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6650">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6650">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6651">7-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6651">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6652">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6652">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6653">連字號或 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6653">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6654">六位數 OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6654">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6655">7-12 個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6655">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6656">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6656">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6657">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6657">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6658">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6658">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6659">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6659">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6660">函數函數Func_jp_sin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6660">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6661">系統找到Keyword_jp_sin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6661">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6662">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6662">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6663">函數函數Func_jp_sin_pre_1997找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6663">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6664">系統找到Keyword_jp_sin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6664">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6665">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6665">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6678">社會保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6678">社会保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6679">介護保険</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6679">介護保険</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6680">介護保険被保険者番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6680">介護保険被保険者番号</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6682">雇用保険被保険者整理番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6682">雇用保険被保険者整理番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6683">厚生年金</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6683">厚生年金</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6684">厚生年金被保険者整理番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6684">厚生年金被保険者整理番号</span></span>


## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6685">拉脫維亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6685">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6686">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6686">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6687">三個字母后面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6687">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6688">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6688">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6689">三個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6689">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6690">三個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6690">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6691">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6691">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6692">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6693">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6693">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6694">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6695">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6696">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6696">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6697">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6697">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6822">拉脫維亞個人代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6822">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6823">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6823">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6824">11 位數及選擇性連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6824">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6825">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6825">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6826">舊格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6826">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6827">11 位數和連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6827">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6828">這是對應到 DD一Y (的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6828">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6829">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6829">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6830">對應至 19 世紀之生產世紀 ("0"、20 世紀對應的 "1" 和 22 世紀) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6830">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6831">隨機產生的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6831">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6832">新格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6832">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6833">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6833">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6834">兩位數 "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6834">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6835">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6835">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6836">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6837">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6837">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6838">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6839">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6839">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6840">函數  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 或 RegEx `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6840">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6841">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6841">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6842">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6842">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6843">函數  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 或 RegEx `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6843">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```
