## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6906">拉脫維亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6906">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6907">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6907">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6908">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6908">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6909">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6909">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6910">兩個字母或數位，後面接著七位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6910">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6911">兩位數或兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6911">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6912">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6912">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6913">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6913">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6914">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6914">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6915">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6915">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6916">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6916">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6917">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6917">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6918">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6918">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6919">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6919">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6920">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6920">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6921">正則運算式會  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6921">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6922">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6922">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6945">立陶宛駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6945">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6946">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6946">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6947">不含空格和分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6947">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6948">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6948">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6949">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6949">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6950">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6950">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6951">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6951">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-6952">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6952">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-6953">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6953">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6954">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6954">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-6955">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-6955">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7080">立陶宛個人代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7080">Lithuania personal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7081">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7081">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7082">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7082">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7083">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7083">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7084">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7084">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7085">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7085">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7086">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7086">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7087">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7087">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7088">不含空格和分隔符號的 11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7088">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7089">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7089">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7090">不含空格和分隔符號的 11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7090">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7091">一位數 (1-6) 表示該人員性別與年齡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7091">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7092">對應至 YYMMDD (出生日期的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7092">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7093">對應至出生日期序列值三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7093">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7094">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7094">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7095">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7095">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7096">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7096">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7097">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7097">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7098">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7098">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7099">此函數  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7099">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7100">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7100">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7101">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7101">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7102">此函數  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7102">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7137">立陶宛護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7137">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7138">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7138">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7139">沒有空格或分隔符號的八位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7139">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7140">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7140">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7141">8 位數或 8 (字母，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7141">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7142">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7142">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7143">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7143">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7144">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7144">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7145">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7145">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7146">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7146">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7147">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7147">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7148">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date3` 尋找 DD MM YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7148">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7149">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7149">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7150">正則運算式會  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7150">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7151">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7151">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">

            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7171">百勝堡駕照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7171">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7172">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7172">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7173">不含空格和分隔符號的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7173">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7174">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7174">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7175">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7175">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7176">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7176">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7177">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7177">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7178">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7178">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7179">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7179">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7180">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7180">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7181">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7181">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7305">奇比堡的國 (號碼) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7305">Luxemburg national identification number (natural persons)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7306">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7306">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7307">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7307">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7308">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7308">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7309">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7309">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7310">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7310">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7311">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7311">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7312">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7313">13 位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7313">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7314">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7314">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7315">13 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7315">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7316">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7316">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7317">兩個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7317">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7318">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7318">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7319">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7319">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7320">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7320">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7321">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7321">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7322">此函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7322">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7323">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7323">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7324">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7324">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7325">此函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7325">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7348">卡比堡護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7348">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7349">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7349">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7350">沒有空格或分隔符號的八位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7350">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7351">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7351">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7352">8 位數或 8 (字母，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7352">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7353">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7353">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7354">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7354">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7355">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7355">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7356">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7356">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7357">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7357">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7358">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7358">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7359">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date3` 尋找 DD MM YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7359">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7360">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7360">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7361">正則運算式會  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7361">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7362">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7362">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7375">Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7375">Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7394">奇比堡國家識別號碼 (非自然人士) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7394">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7395">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7395">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7396">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7396">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7397">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7397">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7398">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7398">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7399">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7399">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7400">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7400">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7401">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7401">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7402">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7402">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7403">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7403">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7404">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7404">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7405">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7405">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7406">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7406">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7407">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7407">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7408">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7408">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7409">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7409">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7410">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7410">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7411">此函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7411">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7412">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7412">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7413">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7413">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7414">此函數  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7414">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7454">馬來西亞識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7454">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7455">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7456">包含選擇性連字號的 12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7456">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7457">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7458">12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7458">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7459">格式為 YYMMDD 的六位數，這是生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7459">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7460">虛線 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7460">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7461">兩個字母的出生日期代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7461">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7462">虛線 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7462">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7463">三個亂數字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7463">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7464">一位數性別代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7464">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7465">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7466">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7466">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7467">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7468">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7468">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7469">正則運算式會Regex_malaysia_id_card_number模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7469">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7470">系統找到Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7470">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7497">盧森堡駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7497">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7498">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7498">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7499">指定模式中兩個字元和六位數的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7499">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7500">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7500">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7501">兩個字元和六位數的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7501">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7502">兩個字元 (或字母，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7502">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7503">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7503">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7504">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7504">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7505">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7505">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7506">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7506">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7507">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7508">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7508">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7509">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7510">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7511">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7511">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7512">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7512">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7636">盧森堡身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7636">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7637">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7637">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7638">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7638">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7639">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7639">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7640">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7640">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7641">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7641">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7642">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7642">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7643">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7643">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7644">七位數後面接著一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7644">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7645">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7645">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7646">七位數，後面接著一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7646">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7647">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7647">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7648">不區分大小寫時，以 "M， G， A， P， L， H， B， Z" 表示 (一個字母) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7648">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7649">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7649">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7650">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7650">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7651">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7651">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7652">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7652">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7653">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7653">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7654">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7654">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7655">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7655">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7656">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7656">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7673">盧森堡護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7673">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7674">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7675">不含空格或分隔符號的七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7675">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7676">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7677">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7677">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7678">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7678">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7679">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7679">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7680">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7680">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7681">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7681">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7682">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7682">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7683">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7683">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7684">找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7684">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7685">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7685">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7686">正則運算式會  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7686">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7687">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7687">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7707">盧森堡稅務識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7707">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7708">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7709">針對馬德群島：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7709">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7710">指定模式中七位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7710">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7711">非馬塞斯群島和馬德群島實體：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7711">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7712">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7712">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7713">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7713">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7714">馬塞文：7 位數和 1 個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7714">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7715">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7715">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7716">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7716">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7717">非馬塞群島和馬德群島：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7717">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7718">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7718">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7719">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7720">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7720">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7721">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7722">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7723">RegEx  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  或 `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7723">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7724">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7724">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7725">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7725">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7726">RegEx  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7726">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7759">荷蘭的服務號碼是 BSN (號碼) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7759">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7760">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7760">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7761">包含選擇性空格的八九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7761">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7762">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7762">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7763">八九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7763">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7764">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7764">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7765">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7765">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7766">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7766">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7767">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7767">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7768">2-3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7768">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7769">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7769">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7770">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7770">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7771">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7771">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7772">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7772">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7773">函數函數Func_netherlands_bsn找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7773">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7774">系統找到Keyword_netherlands_bsn關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7774">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7775">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7775">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7799">荷蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7799">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7800">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7800">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7801">不含空格和分隔符號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7801">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7802">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7802">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7803">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7803">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7804">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7805">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7805">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7806">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7807">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7808">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7808">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7809">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7809">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7937">荷蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7937">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7938">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7938">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7939">九個字母或數位，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7939">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7940">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7940">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7941">九個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7941">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7942">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7942">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7943">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7943">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7944">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7944">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7945">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7945">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7946">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7946">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7947">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7947">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7948">正則運算式會 `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` 尋找 DD MMM/MMM YYYY 格式 (範例 - 26 MAA/MAR 2012) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7948">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7949">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7949">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7950">正則運算式會  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7950">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7951">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7951">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7969">荷蘭稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7969">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7970">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7970">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7971">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7971">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7972">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7972">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7973">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7973">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7974">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7974">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7975">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7975">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7976">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7976">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7977">不含空格或分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7977">nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7978">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7978">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7979">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7979">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7980">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7980">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7981">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7981">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-7982">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7983">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7984">此函數  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7984">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7985">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7985">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-7986">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7986">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-7987">此函數  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-7987">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8025">荷蘭加值稅編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8025">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8026">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8026">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8027">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8027">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8028">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8028">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8029">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8029">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8030">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8030">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8031">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8031">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8032">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8032">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8033">14 個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8033">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8034">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8034">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8035">14 個字元的字母數位元模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8035">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8036">N 或 n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8036">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8037">L 或 l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8037">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8038">選擇性空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8038">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8039">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8039">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8040">選擇性空格、點或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8040">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8041">B 或 b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8041">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8042">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8042">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8043">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8043">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8044">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8044">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8045">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8045">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8046">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8046">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8047">函數函數Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8047">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8048">系統找到Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8048">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8049">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8049">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8050">函數函數Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8050">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8051">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8051">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8059">紐西蘭銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8059">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8060">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8060">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8061">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8061">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8062">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8062">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8063">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8063">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8064">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8064">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8065">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8065">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8066">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8066">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8067">包含選擇性分隔符號的 14 到 16 位數模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8067">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8068">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8068">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8069">包含選擇性分隔符號的 14 到 16 位數模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8069">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8070">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8070">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8071">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8071">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8072">三到四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8072">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8073">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8073">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8074">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8074">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8075">選擇性的連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8075">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8076">2 到 3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8076">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8077">選項連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8077">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8078">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8078">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8079">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8079">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8080">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8080">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8081">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8081">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8082">函數函數Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8082">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8083">系統找到Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8083">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8084">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8084">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8085">函數函數Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8085">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8093">紐西蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8093">New Zealand driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8094">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8094">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8095">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8095">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8096">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8096">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8097">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8097">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8098">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8098">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8099">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8099">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8100">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8100">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8101">八個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8101">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8102">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8102">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8103">八個字元的字母數位元模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8103">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8104">兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8104">two letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8105">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8105">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8106">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8106">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8107">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8107">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8108">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8109">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8110">函數函數Func_newzealand_driver_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8110">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8111">系統找到Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8111">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8112">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8112">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8113">函數函數Func_newzealand_driver_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8113">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8171">驅動程式的分割區#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8171">driver'slicences#</span></span>
