## <a name="new-zealand-inland-revenue-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8180">紐西蘭內陸營收數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8180">New Zealand inland revenue number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8181">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8181">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8182">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8182">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8183">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8183">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8184">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8184">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8185">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8185">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8186">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8186">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8187">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8188">包含選擇性分隔符號的八位數或九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8188">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8189">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8190">包含選擇性分隔符號的八位數或九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8190">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8191">兩位數或三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8191">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8192">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8192">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8193">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8193">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8194">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8194">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8195">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8195">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8196">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8197">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8197">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8198">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8199">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8199">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8200">函數函數Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8200">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8201">系統找到Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8201">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8202">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8202">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8203">函數函數Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8203">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8205">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8205">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8212">紐西蘭健康號碼的開始</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8212">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8213">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8213">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8214">三個字母、一個空格 (選) 和四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8214">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8215">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8215">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8216">三個字母 (除了 'I' 和 'O') 不區分大小寫</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8216">three letters (not case sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8217">這是 (選項) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8217">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8218">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8218">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8219">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8220">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8220">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8221">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8222">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8222">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8223">函數函數Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8223">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8224">系統找到Keyword_nz_terms關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8224">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8225">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8225">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8226">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8227">函數函數Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8227">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8228">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8228">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8242">紐西蘭社會號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8242">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8243">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8243">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8244">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8244">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8245">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8245">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8246">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8246">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8247">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8247">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8248">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8248">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8249">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8249">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8250">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8250">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8251">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8251">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8252">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8252">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8253">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8253">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8254">選擇性的連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8254">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8255">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8255">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8256">選擇性的連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8256">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8257">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8257">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8258">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8258">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8259">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8259">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8260">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8260">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8261">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8261">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8262">函數函數Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8262">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8263">系統找到Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8263">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8264">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8264">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8265">函數函數Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8265">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8267">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8267">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8273">挪威標識號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8273">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8274">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8274">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8275">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8275">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8276">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8276">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8277">11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8277">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8278">格式 DD您用 6 位數表示生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8278">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8279">三位數的個別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8279">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8280">兩個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8280">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8281">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8282">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8282">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8283">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8284">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8284">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8285">函數函數Func_norway_id_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8285">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8286">系統找到Keyword_norway_id_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8286">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8287">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8287">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8288">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8288">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8289">函數函數Func_norway_id_numbe找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8289">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8290">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8290">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8295">識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8295">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8296">識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8296">Identification</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8299">菲律賓統一的多重用途標識號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8299">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8300">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8300">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8301">以連字號分隔的 12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8301">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8302">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8302">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8303">12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8303">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8304">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8304">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8305">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8305">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8306">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8306">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8307">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8307">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8308">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8308">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8309">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8309">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8310">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8310">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8311">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8311">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8312">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8312">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8313">正則運算式會Regex_philippines_unified_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8313">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8314">系統找到Keyword_philippines_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8314">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8315">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8315">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8316">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8316">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8317">統一的多重用途識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8317">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8321">波蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8321">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8322">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8322">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8323">包含 2 個斜線的 14 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8323">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8324">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8324">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8325">14 位數和 2 個斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8325">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8326">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8326">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8327">斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8327">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8328">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8328">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8329">斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8329">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8330">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8330">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8331">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8331">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8332">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8332">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8333">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8333">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8334">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8334">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8335">正則運算式會  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8335">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8336">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8336">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8460">波蘭身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8460">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8461">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8461">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8462">三個字母和六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8462">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8463">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8463">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8464">三個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後面接著六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8464">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8465">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8466">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8467">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8468">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8468">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8469">函數函數Func_polish_national_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8469">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8470">系統找到Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8470">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8471">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8472">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8472">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8476">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8476">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8477">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8477">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8480">道鐘斯指數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8480">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8481">作業系統。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8481">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8482">波蘭國家 (PESEL) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8482">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8483">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8483">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8484">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8484">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8485">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8485">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8486">以 YYMMDD 格式表示生日的 6 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8486">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8487">4 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8487">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8488">1 個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8488">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8489">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8489">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8490">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8490">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8491">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8491">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8492">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8492">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8493">函數函數Func_pesel_identification_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8493">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8494">系統找到Keyword_pesel_identification_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8494">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8495">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8495">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8496">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8496">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8497">函數函數Func_pesel_identification_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8497">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8498">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8498">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8499">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8499">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8500">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8500">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8501">ód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8501">dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8502">ódosobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8502">dowódosobisty</span></span>

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8510">波蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8510">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8511">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼敏感性資訊類型中，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8511">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8512">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8512">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8513">兩個字母及七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8513">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8514">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8514">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8515">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8515">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8516">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8516">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8517">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8517">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8518">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8518">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8519">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8519">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8520">函數函數Func_polish_passport_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8520">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8521">系統找到Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8521">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8522">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8522">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8523">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8523">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8524">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8524">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8525">Numer paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8525">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8526">星期日。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8526">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8527">Paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8527">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8528">Paszport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8528">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8529">波蘭 REGON 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8529">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8530">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8530">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8531">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8531">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8532">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8532">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8533">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8533">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8534">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8534">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8535">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8535">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8536">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8536">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8537">九位數或 14 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8537">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8538">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8539">九位數或 14 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8539">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8540">九位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8540">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8541">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8541">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8542">字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8542">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8543">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8543">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8544">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8545">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8545">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8546">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8547">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8547">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8548">函數函數Func_polish_regon_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8548">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8549">系統找到Keywords_polish_regon_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8549">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8550">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8550">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8551">函數函數Func_polish_regon_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8551">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8568">波蘭稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8568">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8569">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8569">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8570">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8570">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8571">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8571">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8572">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8572">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8573">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8573">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8574">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8574">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8575">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8575">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8576">11 位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8576">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8577">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8578">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8578">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8579">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8580">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8580">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8581">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8582">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8582">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8583">此函數  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8583">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8584">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8584">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
  
```xml
      <!-- Poland Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8614">葡萄牙卡號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8614">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8615">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8615">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8616">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8616">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8617">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8617">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8618">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8618">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8619">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8620">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8621">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8622">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8622">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8623">正則運算式會Regex_portugal_citizen_card找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8623">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8624">系統找到Keyword_portugal_citizen_card關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8624">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8644">葡萄牙駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8644">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8645">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8645">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8646">兩個模式 - 兩個字母后面接著 5 到 8 位數的特殊字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8646">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8647">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8647">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8648">模式 1：兩個字母后面接著 5/6 特殊字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8648">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8649">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8649">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8650">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8650">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8651">五或六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8651">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8652">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8652">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8653">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8653">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8654">模式 2：一個字母后面接著 6/8 位數的特殊字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8654">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8655">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8655">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8656">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8656">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8657">六位或八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8657">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8658">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8658">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8659">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8659">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8660">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8660">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8661">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8661">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8662">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8662">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8663">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8663">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8664">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8664">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8665">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8665">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8797">葡萄牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8797">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8798">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8798">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8799">一個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8799">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8800">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8800">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8801">一個字母后面接著六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8801">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8802">一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8802">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8803">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8803">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8804">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8805">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8805">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8806">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8807">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8807">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8808">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8808">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8809">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8809">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8810">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8810">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8811">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8811">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8812">正則運算式會  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8812">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8813">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8813">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8843">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8843">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8844">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8844">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8845">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8845">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8846">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8846">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8847">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8847">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8848">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8848">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8849">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8849">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8850">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8850">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8851">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8851">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8852">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8852">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8853">此函數  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8853">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8854">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8854">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8855">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8855">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8856">此函數  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8856">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8881">羅馬尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8881">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8882">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8882">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8883">一個字元後面接著八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8883">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8884">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8884">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8885">一個字元後面接著八位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8885">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8886">一個字母 (不區分大小寫的) 數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8886">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8887">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8887">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8888">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8888">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8889">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8889">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-8890">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8890">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-8891">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8891">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8892">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8892">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-8893">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-8893">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9021">羅馬尼亞個人數位代碼 (CNP 格式) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9021">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9022">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9022">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9023">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9023">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9024">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9024">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9025">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9025">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9026">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9026">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9027">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9027">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9028">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9028">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9029">不含空格和分隔符號的 13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9029">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9030">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9030">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9031">1 到 9 的 1 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9031">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9032">代表 YYMMDD (生日的 6 位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9032">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9033">2 位數，可以是 01-52 或 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9033">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9034">4 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9034">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9035">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9035">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9036">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9036">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9037">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9037">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9038">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9038">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9039">此函數  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9039">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9040">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9040">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9041">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9041">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9042">此函數  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9042">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9093">羅馬尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9093">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9094">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9094">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9095">不含空格和分隔符號的八位數或九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9095">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9096">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9096">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9097">8 或 9 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9097">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9098">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9098">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9099">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9099">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9100">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9100">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9101">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9101">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9102">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9102">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9103">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9103">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9104">正則運算式會尋找 `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` 格式 DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) 或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9104">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9105">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9105">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9106">正則運算式會  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9106">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9107">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9107">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9133">十位數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9133">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9134">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9134">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9144">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9144">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9145">RegEx 索引Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9145">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

```xml

          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />

      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9199">沙烏地阿拉伯國名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9199">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9200">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9201">十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9201">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9202">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9203">十個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9203">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9204">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9204">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9205">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9205">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9206">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9206">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9207">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9208">正則運算式會Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9208">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9209">系統找到Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9209">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9214">識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9214">ID number</span></span>

## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9216">新加坡國家註冊身分識別卡 (NRIC) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9216">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9217">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9218">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9218">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9219">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9219">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9220">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9220">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9221">字母 「F」、「G」、「S」或「T」 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9221">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9222">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9222">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9223">字母檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9223">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9224">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9224">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9225">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9225">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9226">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9226">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9227">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9227">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9228">正則運算式會Regex_singapore_nric找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9228">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9229">系統找到Keyword_singapore_nric關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9229">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9230">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9230">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9231">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9231">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9232">正則運算式會Regex_singapore_nric找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9232">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9233">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9233">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9244">斯洛伐克駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9244">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9245">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9245">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9246">一個字元後面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9246">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9247">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9247">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9248">一個字元後面接著七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9248">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9249">一個字母 (不區分大小寫的) 數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9249">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9250">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9250">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9251">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9251">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9252">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9252">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9253">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9253">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9254">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9254">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9255">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9255">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9256">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9256">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
