## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9382">斯洛伐克個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9382">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9383">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9383">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9384">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9384">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9385">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9385">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9386">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9386">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9387">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9387">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9388">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9388">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9389">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9389">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9390">包含選擇性反反杠的九位數或十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9390">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9391">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9391">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9392">代表生日的 6 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9392">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9393">選擇性斜線 (/) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9393">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9394">3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9394">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9395">1 個選擇性的檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9395">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9396">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9397">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9397">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9398">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9399">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9399">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9400">此函數  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9400">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9401">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9401">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9402">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9402">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9403">此函數  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9403">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9450">斯洛伐克護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9450">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9451">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9451">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9452">一位數或一個字母，後面接著七位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9452">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9453">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9453">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9454">一位數或一個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後接七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9454">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9455">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9455">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9456">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9456">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9457">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9457">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9458">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9458">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9459">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9459">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9460">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9460">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9461">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9461">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9462">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9462">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9463">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9463">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9464">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9464">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9486">斯洛洛尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9486">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9487">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9487">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9488">不含空格和分隔符號的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9488">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9489">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9489">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9490">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9490">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9491">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9492">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9492">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9493">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9494">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9494">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9495">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9495">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9496">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9496">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9623">斯洛洛尼亞唯一主要號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9623">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9624">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9624">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9625">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9625">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9626">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9626">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9627">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9627">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9628">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9628">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9629">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9629">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9630">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9630">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9631">不含空格或分隔符號的 13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9631">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9632">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9632">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9633">指定模式中 13 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9633">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9634">對應至 DDMMLLL (的七位數) ，其中 "LLL" 對應至出生日期的最後三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9634">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9635">對應到出生日期 "50" 區的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9635">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9636">三位數對應同一天所生人士的性別與序列值組合 (男性為 000-499，女性為 500-999) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9636">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9637">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9637">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9638">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9638">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9639">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9639">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9640">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9640">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9641">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9641">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9642">此函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9642">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9643">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9643">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9644">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9644">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9645">此函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9645">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9673">斯洛洛尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9673">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9674">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9675">兩個字母后面接著沒有空格或分隔符號的七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9675">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9676">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9677">兩個字母后面接著七位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9677">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9678">字母 "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9678">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9679">一個大寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9679">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9680">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9680">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9681">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9681">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9682">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9682">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9683">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9683">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9684">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9684">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9685">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9685">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9686">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9686">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9687">正則運算式會 `Regex_eu_passport_date1` 尋找 DD.MM.YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9687">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9688">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9689">正則運算式會  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9689">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9690">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9690">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9713">斯洛洛尼亞稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9713">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9714">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9714">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9715">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9715">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9716">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9716">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9717">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9717">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9718">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9718">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9719">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9719">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9720">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9720">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9721">沒有空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9721">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9722">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9722">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9723">1-9 的一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9723">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9724">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9724">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9725">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9725">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9726">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9727">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9727">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9728">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9729">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9730">此函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9730">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9731">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9731">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9732">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9732">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9733">此函數  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9733">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9757">南非標識號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9757">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9758">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9758">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9759">可能包含空格的 13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9759">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9760">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9760">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9761">13 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9761">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9762">格式為 YYMMDD 的六位數，這是生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9762">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9763">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9763">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9764">單位數標記</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9764">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9765">數位 "8" 或 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9765">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9766">一位數是一個檢查碼數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9766">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9767">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9768">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9768">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9769">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9770">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9770">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9771">函數函數Func_south_africa_identification_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9771">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9772">系統找到Keyword_south_africa_identification_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9772">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9773">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9773">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9774">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9774">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_africa_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9775">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9775">Keyword_south_africa_identification_number</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9779">南韓居民註冊號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9779">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9780">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9780">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9781">包含連字號的 13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9781">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9782">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9782">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9783">13 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9783">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9784">格式為 YYMMDD 的六位數，這是生日</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9784">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9785">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9785">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9786">一位數由世紀和性別決定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9786">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9787">四位數地區碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9787">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9788">用來區分前述號碼相同之人的一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9788">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9789">一個檢查數位。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9789">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9790">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9790">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9791">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9791">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9792">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9792">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9793">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9793">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9794">函數函數Func_south_korea_resident_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9794">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9795">系統找到Keyword_south_korea_resident_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9795">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9796">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9796">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9797">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9797">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9798">函數函數Func_south_korea_resident_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9798">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9799">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9799">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9801">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9801">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9807">西班牙駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9807">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9808">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9808">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9809">八位數後面接著一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9809">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9810">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9810">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9811">八位數後面接著一個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9811">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9812">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9812">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9813">一位數或一個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9813">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9814">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9814">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9815">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9815">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9816">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9816">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9817">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9817">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9818">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9818">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9819">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9819">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9820">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9820">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9821">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9821">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-dni"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9955">西班牙 DNI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9955">Spain DNI</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9956">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9956">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9957">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9957">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9958">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9958">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9959">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9959">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9960">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9960">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9961">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9961">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9962">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9962">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9963">八位數後面接著一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9963">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9964">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9964">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9965">七位數後面接著一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9965">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9966">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9966">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9967">選擇性空格或連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9967">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9968">一個檢查 (字母，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9968">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9969">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9969">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9970">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9970">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-9971">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9971">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9972">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9972">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9973">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9973">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9974">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9974">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-9975">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9975">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-9976">函數  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-9976">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10000">西班牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10000">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10001">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10002">字母和數位的八個字元或九個字元組合，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10002">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10003">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10003">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10004">由八個字元或九個字元所組合的字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10004">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10005">兩位數或兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10005">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10006">一位數或一個字母 (選填) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10006">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10007">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10007">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10008">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10008">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10009">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10009">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10010">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10010">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10011">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10011">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10012">正則運算式會  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10012">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10013">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10013">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10014">正則運算式會 `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` 尋找 DD-MM-YYYY 格式的日期，或找到 `Keywords_eu_passport_date` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10014">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10015">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10015">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10016">正則運算式會  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10016">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10017">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10017">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10046">西班牙社會安全號碼 (SSN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10046">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10047">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10047">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10048">11-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10048">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10049">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10049">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10050">11-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10050">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10051">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10051">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10052">斜線 (選填) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10052">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10053">七到八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10053">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10054">斜線 (選填) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10054">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10055">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10055">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10056">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10056">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10057">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10057">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10058">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10058">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10059">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10059">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10060">函數函數Func_spanish_social_security_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10060">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10061">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10061">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Spain SSN -->
<Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10062">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10062">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10063">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10063">None</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10064">西班牙稅務識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10064">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10065">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10065">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10066">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10066">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10067">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10067">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10068">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10068">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10069">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10069">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10070">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10070">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10071">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10071">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10072">指定模式中七位或八位數，以及一或兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10072">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10073">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10073">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10074">具有西班牙國家身分識別卡的西班牙文自然人員：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10074">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10075">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10075">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10076">一個大小寫字母 (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10076">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10077">沒有西班牙身分識別卡的非居民</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10077">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10078">一個大小寫字母"L" (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10078">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10079">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10079">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10080">一個大小寫字母 (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10080">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10081">沒有西班牙身分識別卡且年齡不足 14 歲之居民.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10081">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10082">一個大小寫字母"K" (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10082">one uppercase letter"K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10083">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10083">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10084">一個大小寫字母 (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10084">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10085">有百分位的識別號碼的人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10085">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10086">這是區分大小寫的一個大寫字母「X」、「Y」或「Z」 (大寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10086">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10087">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10087">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10088">一個大小寫字母 (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10088">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10089">沒有百分位人士識別號碼的號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10089">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10090">一個大小寫為「M」的字母， (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10090">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10091">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10091">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10092">一個大小寫字母 (區分大小寫的) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10092">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10093">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10093">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10094">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10094">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10095">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10095">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10096">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10096">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10097">函數  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10097">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10098">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10098">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10099">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10099">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10100">函數  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 或 `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10100">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10131">SQL Server 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10131">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10132">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10133">字串「使用者識別碼」、「使用者識別碼」、「uid」或「UserId」，後面接著下圖中概述的字元和字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10133">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10134">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10134">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10135">字串 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid" 或 "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10135">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10136">1-200 個上下字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10136">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10137">字串 "Password" 或 "pwd"，其中 "pwd" 前面沒有小寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10137">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" is not preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10138">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10138">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10139">任何不是貨幣符號的字元 ($) 、百分比符號 (%) 、大於符號 (>) 、符號 (@) 、引號 (") 、分號 (;) 、左大括弧 ([) 或左中括弧 ({) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10139">any character that is not a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10140">任何 7-128 個字元的組合，不是分號 (;) 、斜線 (/) 或引號 (") </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10140">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10141">分號 (;) 引號 (") </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10141">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10142">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10142">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10143">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10143">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10144">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10144">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10145">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10145">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10146">正則運算式會CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10146">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10147">找不到您CEP_GlobalFilter **關鍵字** 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10147">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter is **not** found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10148">正則運算式 **CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10148">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10149">正則運算式 **CEP_CommonExampleKeywords找不到符合** 模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10149">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10150">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10150">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10151">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10151">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10152">部分密碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10152">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10153">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10153">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10154">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10154">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10155">樣品</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10155">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10156">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10156">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10157"> (請注意，就技術上來說，這種敏感性資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10157">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10158">密碼或 pd 後面接著 0-2 個空格、等號 (=) 、0-2 個空格，以及一個星號 (\*) --OR--</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10158">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) --OR--</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10159">密碼或 ppd 後面接著：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10159">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10160">等號 (=) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10160">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10161">小於符號 (<) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10161">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10162">任何由 1-200 個字元組合成大寫或小寫字母、數位、星號 (\*) 、連字號 (-) 、 (_) 或空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10162">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10163">大於符號 (>) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10163">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10164">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10164">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10165"> (請注意，就技術上來說，這種敏感性資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10165">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10166">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10166">contoso</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10169">沙 箱</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10169">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10170">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10170">onebox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10175">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10175">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10176">網</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10176">net</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10177">瑞典駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10177">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10178">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10178">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10179">包含連字號的十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10179">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10180">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10180">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10181">包含連字號的十位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10181">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10182">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10182">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10183">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10183">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10184">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10184">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10185">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10186">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10186">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10187">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10188">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10188">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10189">正則運算式會  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10189">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10190">關鍵字來自  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 或找到。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10190">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10323">瑞典國識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10323">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10324">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10324">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10325">十位數或 12 位數以及選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10325">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10326">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10326">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10327">十位數或 12 位數以及選擇性分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10327">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10328">兩位數 (選) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10328">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10329">日期格式 YYMMDD 的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10329">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10330">選擇性選項之 "-" 或 "+" (分隔) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10330">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10331">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10331">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10332">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10333">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10333">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10334">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10334">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10335">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10335">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10336">此函數 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10336">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10337">找到 `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` 關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10337">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10338">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10338">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10339">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10339">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10340">此函數 `Func_swedish_national_identifier` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10340">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10341">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10341">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10360">瑞典護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10360">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10361">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼敏感性資訊類型中，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10361">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10362">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10362">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10363">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10363">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10364">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10364">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10365">八個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10365">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10366">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10366">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10367">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10367">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10368">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10368">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10369">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10369">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10370">正則運算式會Regex_sweden_passport_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10370">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10371">下列其中一個條件成立：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10371">one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10372">找到您Keyword_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10372">a keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10373">找到您Keyword_sweden_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10373">a keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
