## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10404">瑞典稅務識別編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10404">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10405">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10405">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10406">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10406">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10407">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10407">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10408">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10408">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10409">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10409">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10410">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10410">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10411">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10412">指定圖樣中的十位數和符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10412">ten digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10413">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10414">十位數和一個符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10414">ten digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10415">對應至 YYMMDD (的六位數) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10415">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10416">加號或減號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10416">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10417">讓識別號碼獨一無二的三位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10417">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10418">對於 1990 之前所發行的數位，第七位數和第八位數會指出出生日期或外縣/市</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10418">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10419">第九個位置的位數會以奇數表示男性或甚至女性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10419">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10420">一個檢查數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10420">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10421">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10421">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10422">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10422">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10423">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10423">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10424">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10424">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10425">此函數  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10425">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10426">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10426">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10427">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10427">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10428">此函數  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10428">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10454">SWIFT 代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10454">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10455">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10456">四個字母，後面接著 5-31 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10456">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10457">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10458">四個字母，後面接著 5-31 個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10458">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10459">四個字母的銀行帳戶 (大小寫不區分) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10459">four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10460">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10460">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10461">BBAN (基本銀行帳戶號碼 (4-28) ) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10461">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10462">一個選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10462">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10463">BBAN (餘數的 1 到 3) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10463">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10464">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10464">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10465">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10465">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10466">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10466">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10467">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10467">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10468">正則運算式會Regex_swift找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10468">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10469">系統找到Keyword_swift關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10469">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10506">瑞士 SSN AHV 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10506">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10507">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10507">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10508">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10508">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10509">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10509">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10510">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10510">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10511">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10511">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10512">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10512">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10513">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10514">13 位數號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10514">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10515">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10516">13 位數號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10516">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10517">三位數 - 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10517">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10518">選擇性的點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10518">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10519">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10519">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10520">選擇性的點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10520">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10521">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10521">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10522">選擇性的點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10522">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10523">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10523">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10524">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10524">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10525">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10525">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10526">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10526">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10527">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10527">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10528">函數函數Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10528">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10529">系統找到Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10529">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10530">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10530">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10531">函數函數Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10531">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10552">臺灣國標識號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10552">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10553">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10553">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10554">一個字母 (英文) 後面接著九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10554">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10555">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10555">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10556">一個字母 (英文) 後面接著九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10556">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10557">一個字母 (英文，不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10557">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10558">數位 "1" 或 "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10558">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10559">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10559">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10560">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10560">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10561">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10561">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10562">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10562">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10563">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10563">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10564">函數函數Func_taiwanese_national_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10564">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10565">系統找到Keyword_taiwanese_national_id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10565">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10566">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10566">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10567">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10567">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10568">函數函數Func_taiwanese_national_id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10568">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10569">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10569">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10586">臺灣護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10586">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10587">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10587">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10588">護照號碼：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10588">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10589">非護照號碼：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10589">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10590">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10590">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10591">護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10591">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10592">字元 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10592">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10593">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10593">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10594">非護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10594">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10595">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10595">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10596">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10596">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10597">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10597">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10598">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10598">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10599">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10599">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10600">正則運算式會Regex_taiwan_passport找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10600">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10601">系統找到Keyword_taiwan_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10601">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10612">臺灣居民憑證 (ARC/TARC) 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10612">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10613">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10613">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10614">十個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10614">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10615">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10615">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10616">十個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10616">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10617">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10617">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10618">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10618">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10619">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10620">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10621">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10622">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10622">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10623">正則運算式會Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10623">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10624">系統找到Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10624">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10625">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10625">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10638">泰文人口識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10638">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10639">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10640">13 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10640">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10641">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10642">13 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10642">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10643">第一位數不是零或九</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10643">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10644">12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10644">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10645">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10645">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10646">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10646">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10647">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10647">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10648">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10648">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10649">函數函數Func_Thai_Citizen_Id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10649">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10650">系統找到Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10650">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10651">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10651">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10652">函數函數Func_Thai_Citizen_Id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10652">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10661">土耳其文國家識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10661">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10662">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10663">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10663">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10664">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10665">11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10665">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10666">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10666">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10667">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10667">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10668">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10668">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10669">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10669">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10670">函數函數Func_Turkish_National_Id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10670">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10671">系統找到Keyword_Turkish_National_Id關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10671">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10672">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10672">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10673">函數函數Func_Turkish_National_Id找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10673">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10680">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10680">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10681">駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10681">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10682">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在歐盟駕照編號敏感性資訊類型中，且可做為獨立敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10682">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10683">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10683">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10684">以指定格式結合 18 個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10684">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10685">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10685">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10686">18 個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10686">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10687">五個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位 "9" 來表示字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10687">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10688">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10688">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10689">如果驅動程式是女性 (，即 51 到 62，而不是 01 到 12) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10689">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10690">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 或數位 "9" 來表示字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10690">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10691">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10691">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10692">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10693">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10693">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10694">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10695">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10696">函數函數Func_uk_drivers_license找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10696">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10697">系統找到Keyword_uk_drivers_license關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10697">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10698">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10698">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10704">車用車</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10704">motor cars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10706">side轉場</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10706">sidecar</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10707">三輪車</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10707">tricycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10708">摩托車</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10708">motorcycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10709">photocard 授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10709">photocard licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10710">學習者驅動程式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10710">learner drivers</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10713">駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10713">driving licences</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10714">駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10714">driving licence</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10715">雙重控制車</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10715">dual control car</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10716">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10716">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10717">側卷號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10717">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10718">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10719">兩個字母，後面接著 1 到 4 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10719">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10720">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10721">兩個字母 (不區分大小寫) 後面接著 1 到 4 個數字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10721">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10722">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10722">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10723">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10723">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10724">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10724">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10725">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10725">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10726">正則運算式會Regex_uk_electoral找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10726">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10727">系統找到Keyword_uk_electoral關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10727">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10734">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10734">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10735">國家健康服務編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10735">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10736">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10736">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10737">以空格分隔的 10-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10737">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10738">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10738">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10739">10-17 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10739">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10740">三位數或十位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10740">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10741">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10741">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10742">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10742">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10743">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10743">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10744">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10744">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10745">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10746">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10747">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10748">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10749">函數函數Func_uk_nhs_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10749">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10750">下列其中一個條件成立：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10750">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10751">系統找到Keyword_uk_nhs_number關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10751">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10752">系統找到Keyword_uk_nhs_number1關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10752">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10753">系統找到Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10753">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10754">會傳遞檢查和。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10754">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10772">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10772">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10773">國家保險編號 (NINO) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10773">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10774">此敏感性資訊類型實體包含在 EU National Identificaiton 數位敏感性資訊類型中，而且可做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10774">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10775">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10775">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10776">以空格或虛線分隔的七個字元或九個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10776">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10777">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10777">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10778">兩種可能的模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10778">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10779">兩個字母 (有效的 NINOS 只會使用此首碼中的特定字元，此模式會驗證此字元;不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10779">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10780">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10780">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10781">如前詞一樣使用 'A'、'B'、C 或 'D' (，尾碼中只允許特定字元;不區分大小寫) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10781">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10782">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10782">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10783">兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10783">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10784">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10784">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10785">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10785">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10786">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10786">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10787">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10787">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10788">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10788">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10789">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10789">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10790">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10790">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10791">可以是 'A'、'B'、'C' 或 'D'</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10791">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10792">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10792">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10793">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10793">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10794">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10794">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10795">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10795">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10796">函數函數Func_uk_nino找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10796">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10797">系統找到Keyword_uk_nino關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10797">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10798">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10798">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10799">函數函數Func_uk_nino找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10799">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10821">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10821">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10822">唯一的稅務參考編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10822">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10823">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10823">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10824">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10824">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10825">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10825">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10826">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10826">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10827">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10827">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10828">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10828">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10829">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10829">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10830">不含空格和分隔符號的 10 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10830">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10831">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10831">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10832">10 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10832">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10833">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10833">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10834">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10834">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10835">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10835">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10836">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10836">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10837">此函數  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 會尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10837">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10838">找到關鍵字  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10838">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10858">美國銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10858">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10859">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10860">6-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10860">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10861">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10862">6-17 個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10862">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10863">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10864">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10864">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10865">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10866">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10866">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10867">正則運算式會Regex_usa_bank_account_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10867">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10868">系統找到Keyword_usa_Bank_Account關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10868">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10898">美國駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10898">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10899">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10900">依省/市</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10900">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10901">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10902">取決於州/省，例如紐約：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10902">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10903">格式為 ddd ddd d 的九位數會相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10903">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10904">九位數 ，例如 dddd 不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10904">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10905">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10906">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10906">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-10907">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10908">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10909">函數函數Func_new_york_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10909">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10910">系統找到 Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10910">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10911">系統找到Keyword_us_drivers_license關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10911">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-10912">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10912">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10913">函數函數Func_new_york_drivers_license_number找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10913">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10914">系統找到 Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10914">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10915">系統找到Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10915">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-10916">找不到來自Keyword_us_drivers_license關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-10916">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11014">ITIN (美國 (稅務) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11014">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11015">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11016">以 "9" 開頭且包含 "7" 或 "8" 做為第四位數的九位數，可選擇性地格式化為空格或虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11016">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11017">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11018">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11018">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11019">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11019">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11020">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11020">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11021">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11021">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11022">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11022">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11023">一位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11023">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11024">空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11024">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11025">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11025">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11026">未格式化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11026">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11027">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11027">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11028">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11028">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11029">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11029">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11030">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11030">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11031">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11031">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11032">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11032">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11033">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11033">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11034">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11034">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11035">函數函數Func_formatted_itin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11035">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11036">系統找到Keyword_itin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11036">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11037">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11037">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11038">函數函數Func_unformatted_itin找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11038">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11039">系統找到Keyword_itin關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11039">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11040">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11040">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11041">函數會Func_formatted_itin或Func_unformatted_itin尋找符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11041">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11042">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11042">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11043">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11043">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11044">納稅人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11044">taxpayer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11045">稅務識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11045">tax id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11046">稅務識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11046">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11047">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11047">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11048">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11048">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11049">Ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11049">ssn</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11050">錫</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11050">tin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11051">社會保障</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11051">social security</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11052">納稅人</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11052">tax payer</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11053">itins</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11053">itins</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11054">已刪除</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11054">taxid</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11055">個人稅務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11055">individual taxpayer</span></span> 


## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11056">美國社會安全號碼 (SSN) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11056">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11057">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11058">九位數，可能是格式已格式化或未格式化的圖樣</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11058">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11059">如果在 2011 年中之前發行，SSN 具有強大的格式，其中數位的某些部分必須落在特定範圍內才能有效 (但沒有檢查) 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11059">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11060">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11061">四個函數會以四種不同的模式尋找 SSN：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11061">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11062">Func_ssn SSN 具有 2011 之前強式格式，格式已格式化為虛線或空格 (ddd-dd-dd OR ddd dd dd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11062">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11063">Func_unformatted_ssn 2011 之前格式未格式化為九位數的 SSN (ddddd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11063">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11064">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn會找出格式為虛線或空格的 2011 後 SSN (ddd-dd OR ddd dd dd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11064">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11065">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn 2011 後 SSN 會找出未格式化為九位數的連續數位 (dddd) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11065">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11066">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11066">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11067">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11067">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11068">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11068">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11069">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，會非常信賴地偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11069">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11070">函數函數Func_ssn找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11070">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11071">系統找到Keyword_ssn關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11071">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11072">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11072">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11073">函數函數Func_unformatted_ssn找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11073">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11074">系統找到Keyword_ssn關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11074">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11075">DLP 政策在鄰近 300 個字元時，可偵測到這類敏感性資訊的信賴度較低：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11075">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11076">函數函數Func_randomized_formatted_ssn找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11076">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11077">系統找到Keyword_ssn關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11077">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11078">如果鄰近 300 個字元，DLP 政策 55% 可確信它可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11078">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11079">函數函數Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11079">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11080">系統找到Keyword_ssn關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11080">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11095">美國/英國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11095">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11096">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11096">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11097">英國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11097">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11098">護照號碼的敏感性資訊類型實體可在歐盟護照號碼敏感性資訊類型中提供，並做為獨立的敏感性資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11098">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11099">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11099">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11100">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11100">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11101">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11101">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11102">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11102">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11103">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11104">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11104">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11105">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11106">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11106">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11107">函數函數Func_usa_uk_passport找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11107">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11108">系統找到Keyword_passport關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11108">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11129">烏克蘭護照國內</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11129">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11130">此敏感性資訊類型僅適用于：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11130">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11131">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11131">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11132">通訊合規性政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11132">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11133">資訊管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11133">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11134">記錄管理</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11134">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11135">Microsoft 雲端 App 安全性</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11135">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11136">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11136">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11137">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11137">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11138">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11138">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11139">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11139">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11140">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11140">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11141">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11141">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11142">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11142">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11143">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11143">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11144">RegEx 索引Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11144">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11145">系統找到Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11145">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11156">資料外遺失防護政策</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11156">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11161">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11161">Format</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11169">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11169">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="4056e-11170">DLP 策略在鄰近 300 個字元時，有中度信賴度可偵測到這類敏感性資訊：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11170">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11171">RegEx Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11171">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="4056e-11172">系統找到Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11172">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="4056e-11173">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="4056e-11173">Keywords</span></span>
